le)%20comment%20%26quot%3Bmy%20position%20(in%20ISRO)%20was%20threatened...%20I%20could%20have%20been%20thrown%20out%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20don't%20think%20everything%20was%20nice%20for%20me%20in%20my%20life...%20I%20also%20faced%20challenges%20in%20personal%20life%20and%20official%20life.%20You%20(referring%20to%20himself)%20can%20be%20thrown%20out%20of%20an%20organisation...%20your%20position%20can%20be%20threatened%20(and)%20you%20are%20sometimes%20not%20even%20treated%20with%20great%20respect%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20on%20his%20career%2C%20India's%20top%20space%20man%20recalled%20harsh%20words%20ahead%20of%20an%20earlier%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20years%20ago...%20in%20launch%20of%20PSLV%20Mark-III%20expedition%20there%20was%20every%20possibility%20of%20a%20failure%20but%20somebody%20had%20to%20take%20the%20decision%20(of%20launching)%20and%20I%20took%20it.%20I%20think%20I%20was%20threatened...%20that%20it%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bcolossal%20failure%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E'But%20there%20was%20nobody%20else%20and%20I%20did%20it...%20and%20it%20was%20successful.%20Many%20things%20happen%20in%20life%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-updates-isro-satisfied-with-data-isro-chief-s-somanath-discusses-chandrayaan-3-challenges-%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20Must%20Have%20Permanent%20Habitat%20On%20Moon%20And%20Mars%3A%20ISRO%20Chief%20To%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ISRO%20boss%2C%20with%20a%20smile%20on%20his%20face%2C%20said%20that%20though%20he%20had%20been%20criticised%20and%20his%20ability%20questioned%2C%20he%20had%20taught%20himself%20to%20rise%20above%20the%20%26quot%3Bsilly%20words...%20silly%20acts%26quot%3B%20of%20some%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'...you%20are%20not%20a%20suitable%20person%20(for%20this%20role)'...%20I%20hear%20all%20this%20criticism%20but%20you%20have%20to%20raise%20yourself%20above%20these%20silly%20things.%20Once%20you%20reach%20that%20point%20(of%20self-confidence)%20you%20can%20look%20at%20people%20like%20this%20and%20smile.%20Their%20silly%20acts%20can%20be%20ignored.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwork-of-a-generation-isro-chief-on-chandrayaan-3s-moon-landing-4323123%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWork%20Of%20A%20Generation%26quot%3B%3A%20ISRO%20Chief%20On%20Chandrayaan-3's%20Moon%20Landing%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20to%20do%20that%3F%20You%20go%20through%20a%20process...%20learn%20how%20to%20develop%20your%20self-confidence.%20And%20once%20you%20do%20that%20then%20you%20are%20not%20worried%20about%20these%20silly%20people%20and%20their%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20who%20made%20India's%20wildest%20space%20dreams%20a%20reality%20is%20soft-spoken%20and%20erudite%2C%20and%20describes%20himself%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bexplorer%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20explore%20the%20Moon...%20the%20inner%20space.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20the%20journey%20of%20my%20life%20to%20explore%20science%20and%20spirituality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20temple%20after%20Chandrayaan-3%20landed%20on%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20%26quot%3Bjourney%26quot%3B%20involves%20an%20understanding%20of%20one's%20weaknesses%20and%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpart-of-my-journey-to-explore-both-science-and-spirituality-isro-chief-s-somanath-4335035%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BI%20Explore%20Both%20Science%20And%20Spirituality%26quot%3B%3A%20ISRO%20Chief%20On%20Temple%20Visit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Somanath%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20several%20limitations...%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20technical%20capabilities%20and%20my%20own%20personal%20capacity.%20You%20work%20on%20this%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%20in%20your%20own%20way.%20For%20me%2C%20my%20mental%20and%20physical%20growth%20and%20subject%20knowledge%20growth%20was%20thanks%20to%20various%20people%20who%20came%20in%20my%20life%20at%20different%20times%20and%20gave%20me%20insight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EOn%20India%20Habitat%20On%20Moon%2C%20Mars%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20India's%20future%20space%20plans%20-%20which%20include%20the%20Aditya%20L1%20solar%20and%20manned%20Gaganyaan%20mission%20-%20Mr%20Somanath%20said%20if%20humanity%20plans%20to%20travel%20beyond%20Earth%2C%20habitat%20creation%20is%20needed%20on%20the%20Moon%20and%20Mars%2C%20as%20well%20as%20exoplanets%2C%20and%20that%20Indians%20had%20to%20be%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20of%20ourselves%20as%20so%20inferior%20today...%20that%20we%20are%20not%20technologically%20advanced%2C%20not%20financially%20powerful.%20And%20we%20always%20think%20we%20are%20poor%2C%20so%20we%20can't%20invest%20in%20all%20of%20this.%20I%20believe%20that%20this%20has%20to%20go%2C%20for%20a%20nation%20which%20thinks%20that%20they%20are%20the%20one%20who%20are%20creators%20of%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695634980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fsi9cgr68_isro-chief-_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-news-s-somanath-isro-chief-to-ndtv-could-have-been-thrown-out-isro-chief-recalls-challenges-in-career-4421531%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20the%20points%20the%20ISRO%20Chairperson%20discussed%20were%20the%20many%20challenges%20he%20has%20faced%20over%20the%20course%20of%20his%20career%2C%20including%20(the%20now%20scarcely%20believable)%20contention%20%26quot%3Bmy%20position%20(in%20ISRO)%20was%20threatened...%20I%20could%