0yearend%20state%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20In%20his%20big%20outreach%20to%20women%20voters%20at%20the%20Bhopal%20rally%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20%26quot%3Bguaranteed%26quot%3B%20to%20fulfil%20all%20BJP%20promises%20if%20his%20party%20returns%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20%3Cem%3Eghamandia%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealliance%20reluctantly%20supported%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PM%20Modi%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20new%20legislation%20reserving%2033%25%20seats%20for%20women%20in%20central%20and%20state%20legislatures.%20The%20Bill%20is%20pending%20the%20President's%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20intentions%20are%20wrong.%20Once%20they%20get%20an%20opportunity%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Eghamandia%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealliance%20will%20betray%20the%20mothers%20and%20sisters%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20the%20Congress%20is%20now%20being%20run%20by%20%26quot%3BUrban%20Naxals%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20term%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20refer%20loosely%20to%20those%20accused%20of%20helping%20the%20ultra-Left.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20is%20now%20a%20company%20that%20outsources%20everything%20-%20slogans%20to%20policy%20-%20to%20the%20Urban%20Naxals%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20attacked%20the%20previous%20Congress%20governments%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20for%20not%20keeping%20its%20election%20promises%20in%20the%20past.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20Modi's%20guarantee%20to%20fulfil%20all%20guarantees%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20asserting%20that%20unlike%20the%20Congress%20his%20party%20will%20fulfil%20all%20promises%20that%20it%20makes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20did%20nothing%20for%20women%2C%20PM%20Modi%20continued%2C%20and%20that%20he%20made%20toilets%20and%20implemented%20women-centric%20schemes%20like%20the%20Ujjwala%20Yojana.%20The%20BJP%20works%20for%20development%20while%20the%20Congress%20works%20for%20votes%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20ruled%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20for%20many%20years%2C%20but%20the%20youth%20in%20the%20state%20witnessed%20misrule%2C%20corruption%2C%20and%20poor%20law%20and%20order.%20They%20are%20against%20every%20project%20made%20for%20a%20developed%20India%20and%20has%20no%20thought%20process%20for%20the%20future.%20The%20Congress%20made%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20a%20bimaru%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBIMARU%20(which%20means%20ailing%20in%20literal%20sense)%20-%20the%20acronym%20has%20often%20been%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20Bihar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20to%20imply%20that%20these%20states%20lagged%20in%20terms%20of%20economic%20growth%2C%20healthcare%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20kept%20people%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%20for%20votes%20and%20wants%20to%20take%20India%20back%20to%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20is%20a%20dynastic%20party%20with%20a%20history%20of%20corruption%20and%20appeasement.%20It%20is%20like%20a%20rusted%20iron%20that%20will%20be%20finished%20if%20kept%20in%20the%20rain%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leaders%20are%20born%20with%20silver%20spoons%20and%20the%20problems%20of%20the%20poor%20is%20adventure%20tourism%20for%20them%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20colonies%20of%20the%20poor%20have%20turned%20into%20picnic%20spots%20and%20poor%20farmers%20fields%20have%20become%20location%20of%20video%20shoots%20for%20Congress%20leaders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Congress%20criticizes%20every%20move%20of%20the%20government%20even%20when%20the%20world%20praises%20those%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20criticised%20the%20BJP's%20railway%20infrastructure%20push.%20They%20also%20criticized%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20despite%20the%20entire%20nation%20praising%20it.%20They%20opposed%20digital%20payment%2C%20but%20the%20world%20is%20impressed%20by%20UPI.%20Congress%20neither%20wants%20to%20change%20nor%20wants%20the%20country%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20the%20Congress%20promised%20to%20eradicate%20poverty%2050%20years%20ago%20but%20it%20failed%20miserably.%20%26quot%3BWill%20you%20want%20to%20make%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20a%20sick%20state%20again%20as%20it%20was%20in%20the%20Congress%20era%3F%20Do%20want%20to%20see%20your%20state%20being%20looted%20by%20the%20corrupt%20party%20again%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695634680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fjoq16tsg_pm-modi-in-bhopal_625x300_25_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fghamandia-alliance-reluctantly-supported-womens-bill-pm-modi-in-bhopal-4421173%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Moditoday%20tore%20into%20the%20opposition's%20%26quot%3Bghamandia%20(arrogant)%26quot%3B%20alliance%20at%20a%20mega%20BJP%20event%20ahead%20of%20the%20yearend%20state%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fghamandia-alliance-reluctantly-supported-womens-bill-pm-modi-in-bhopal-4421173%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fghamandia-alliance-reluctantly-supported-womens-bill-pm-modi-in-bhopal-4421173%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fghamandia-alliance-reluctantly-supported-womens-bill-pm-modi-in-bhopal-4421173%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20India-Canada%20Row%2C%20A%20Look%20At%20Khalistani%20Terrorist's%20'Pakistan%20Links'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanada-based%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Arshdeep%20Dalla%20has%20links%20with%20Pakistan-base