ce%20that%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20Suhail%20and%20Dalla%2C%20they%20murdered%20a%20Hindu%20boy%20at%20Delhi's%20Jahangirpuri%20and%20chopped%20off%20his%20head.%20They%20also%20recorded%20a%20video%20and%20sent%20it%20to%20Suhail%20and%20Dalla.%20Police%20sources%20had%20then%20said%20Naushad%20and%20Jagga%20had%20sent%20the%20video%20to%20%26quot%3Bprove%20their%20loyalty%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20they%20had%20received%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20committing%20the%20heinous%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20his%20period%20of%20absconding%20accused%20Jagjit%20Singh%20%40%20Jagga%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20designated%20Khalistani%20Terrorist%20Arshdeep%20%40%20Arsh%20Dala%20who%20had%20instructed%20him%20to%20murder%20some%20leaders%20of%20RSS%20and%20the%20prominent%20persons%20who%20are%20against%20the%20Khalistani%20Movement%20in%20Punjab.%20A%20nexus%20had%20developed%20between%20Pakistan-based%20Suhail%2C%20Naushad%2C%20Jagjit%20Singh%20%40%20Jagga%20and%20Arshdeep%20%40%20Arsh%20Dala%20to%20commit%20terror%20activities%20on%20the%20instruction%20of%20LeT%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20designated%20terrorist%20Arsh%20Dala%20in%20Punjab%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20chargesheet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20been%20tasked%20to%20kill%20Sadhus%2F%20Religious%20leaders%20and%20also%20commit%20targeted%20killings%20in%20Punjab%20for%20which%20they%20have%20received%20money%2C%20weapons%20from%20Suhail%20and%20Arshdeep%20%40%20Dala%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDalla%2C%20sources%20have%20said%2C%20had%20the%20complete%20backing%20of%20Pakistan's%20ISI%20and%20Lashkar-e-Taiba.%C2%A0It%20is%20also%20learnt%20that%20Dalla%20was%20close%20to%20Nijjar%20and%20to%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Sukhdool%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20killed%20in%20a%20gang%20war%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDalla%2C%2027%2C%20is%20from%20Moga%20d