0accused%20to%20escape%20from%20the%20police%20who%20were%20focused%20on%20avoiding%20the%20attacks%20of%20the%20canines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20dogs%20were%20subdued%20and%20over%2017%20kilograms%20of%20ganja%20was%20seized%20from%20the%20site%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Kottayam%20SP%20K%20Karthick%20IPS%20said%20it%20was%20close%20to%20midnight%20when%20the%20search%20team%2C%20also%20comprising%20officers%20from%20the%20nearby%20Gandhinagar%20police%20station%2C%20arrived%20at%20the%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20not%20expect%20there%20would%20be%20so%20many%20dogs%20here%20and%20that%20they%20would%20be%20violent.%20So%2C%20we%20faced%20difficulty%20initially%20in%20carrying%20out%20a%20proper%20search.%20Fortunately%2C%20none%20of%20the%20officers%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20had%20imparted%20training%20to%20the%20dogs%20to%20bite%20on%20seeing%20khaki.%20He%20had%20been%20briefly%20trained%20in%20dog%20handling%20by%20a%20person%20retired%20from%20the%20BSF%2C%20but%20was%20kicked%20out%20from%20there%20for%20asking%20questions%20like%20how%20to%20make%20dogs%20bite%20someone%20wearing%20khaki%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20SP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20officer%20of%20the%20district%20police%20also%20said%20the%20accused%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20being%20a%20dog%20trainer%20was%20selling%20drugs%20and%20the%20same%20was%20evident%20from%20the%20seizure%20of%20over%2017%20kgs%20of%20ganja%20from%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20our%20preliminary%20investigation%2C%20he%20(accused)%20was%20living%20here%20on%20rent%20and%20was%20known%20to%20everyone%20in%20the%20area%20as%20a%20dog%20trainer.%20Therefore%2C%20people%20used%20to%20leave%20their%20dogs%20with%20him%2C%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20day%2C%20when%20they%20went%20outside%20and%20he%20would%20look%20after%20the%20canines%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20K