nd-grimes-amber-heard-new-biography-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695632281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65046adab8708d001927bca0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-worst-boyfriend-grimes-amber-heard-new-biography-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What's%20it%20like%20to%20date%20the%20richest%20man%20in%20the%20world%3F%20It's%20not%20all%20glitz%20and%20glamour.%20A%20new%20biography%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20paints%20a%20somewhat%20sobering%20picture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gkay%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Kay)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A70%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-worst-boyfriend-grimes-amber-heard-new-biography-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20As%20Canada%20Messes%20Up%20Indo-Pacific%20Strategy%2C%20China%20Has%20Last%20Laugh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20long%20accused%20China%20of%20meddling%20in%20its%20domestic%20affairs%2C%20and%20the%20charges%20range%20from%20election%20interference%20to%20money%20laundering%20to%20counterfeiting%20and%20so%20on.%20The%20allegations%20go%20as%20far%20back%20as%20a%201997%20report%20from%20the%20Canadian%20Security%20Intelligence%20Service%2C%20and%20the%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20(RCMP)%2C%20which%20warned%20of%20a%20collaboration%20between%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20(CCP)%20officials%2C%20criminals%2C%20mafia%20and%20business%20tycoons%20to%20infiltrate%20Canadian%20businesses%2C%20to%20steal%20intellectual%20property%20rights%20and%20to%20interfere%20in%20the%20management%20of%20the%20country.%20While%20many%20of%20the%20Canadian%20accusations%2C%20along%20with%20the%20evidence%2C%20have%20been%20missed%20by%20the%20world%20media%20at%20large%2C%20Meng%20Wanzhou's%20arrest%20in%202019%20made%20global%20headlines.%20The%20RCMP%2C%20on%20a%20warrant%20from%20US%20officials%2C%20arrested%20Huawei%20executive%20Meng%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20company's%20founder.%20Meng%2C%20the%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20of%20Huawei%2C%20was%20accused%20of%20violating%20US%20sanctions%20on%20Iran.%20China%20retaliated%20and%20unleashed%20hostage%20diplomacy%2C%20arresting%20two%20Canadians%20in%20China%20on%20charges%20of%20espionage.%20The%20crisis%20in%20Canada-China%20relations%20lasted%20till%202021%2C%20when%20Meng's%20case%20was%20dismissed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20Canada%20unveiled%20its%20Indo-Pacific%20strategy%20with%20a%20sharp%20focus%20on%20China.%20The%20strategy%20not%20just%20outlines%20the%20China%20challenge%20with%20concerns%20about%20Chinese%20strategic%20and%20motivated%20investments%2C%20coercive%20approaches%2C%20arbitrary%20application%20of%20laws%2C%20and%20military%20capabilities%2C%20but%20it%20also%20plans%20to%20review%20all%20existing%20mechanisms%20and%20structures%20with%20China%20and%20diversify%20its%20investments%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20India-Pacific%20strategy%20identifies%20India%20as%20a%20critical%20partner%20and%20delves%20into%20specific%20areas%20for%20enhancing%20cooperation.%20However%2C%20all%20came%20to%20naught%20as%20Canada%20unleashed%20accusations%20against%20India%20this%20month%2C%20without%20offering%20any%20evidence%20of%20New%20Delhi's%20role%20in%20exterminating%20a%20so-called%20Canadian%20citizen%20on%20its%20soil.%20While%20India%20has%20condemned%20the%20baseless%20allegation%2C%20and%20Justin%20Trudeau%20hasn't%20provided%20any%20evidence%20in%20seven%20days%2C%20let%20alone%20concrete%20evidence%2C%20China%20laughs%20the%20last%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20disinformation%20and%20propaganda%20abounds%2C%20tracking%20the%20most%20dominant%20narratives%20in%20state-controlled%20societies%20with%20complete%20surveillance%20of%20social%20media%20-%20as%20is%20the%20case%20in%20China%20-%20becomes%20useful%20in%20order%20to%20understand%20the%20discourse.%20The%20news%20website%20of%20the%20Chinese%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%2C%20even%20before%20Trudeau%20levelled%20his%20allegations%20against%20India%2C%20published%20several%20articles%20on%20deteriorating%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20and%20noted%20that%20Trudeau's%20visit%20to%20India%20for%20the%20G20%20summit%20was%20extremely%20low%20key.%20It%20also%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20accusations%20of%20terrorist%20activities%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20are%20targeted%20at%20India's%20minority%20community%20-%20the%20Sikhs.%20Clearly%2C%20the%20narrative%20equates%20Sikhs%20with%20terrorist%20outfits%20in%20Canada%20-%20something%20that%20India%20has%20never%20said.%20The%20same%20website%20also%20has%20articles%20on%20the%20postponement%20of%20a%20Canadian%20trade%20delegation%20to%20India.%20While%20the%20fact%20is%20true%20that%20the%20delegation's%20visit%20was%20postponed%2C%20the%20narrative%20pushed%20out%20again%20by%20the%20articles%20on%20the%20so-called%20news%20website%20is%20that%20India%20was%20concerned%20about%20Sikhs%20in%20Canada%2C%20which%20is%20entirely%20untrue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20Huanqiu%20and%20its%20English%20version%2C%20the%20Global%20Times%2C%20have%20come%20up%20with%20several%20%26quot%3Bcommentaries%26quot%3B%20on%20how%20the%20India-US%20partnership%20is%20unravelling%2C%20and%20how%20India%20needs%20to%20understand%20it%20can%20never%20be%20treated%20as%20an%20equal%20partner%20by%20the%20West.%20What%20is%20implicit%20is%20that%20India%20should%20give%20up%20its%20sovereignty-related%20disputes%20with%20China%20and%20join%20hands%20with%20it%20in%20a%20campaign%20against%20the%20West.%20What%20is%20conveniently%20ignored%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20in%20all%20propaganda%2C%20is%20that%20India%20has%20always%20preferred%20to%20stay%20neutral%2C%20even%20in%20the%20most%20difficult%20situations%2C%20and%20has%20relied%20on%20its%20own%20strengths%20to%20navigate%20crises%20in%20international%20politics.%20The%20%26quot%3BIndia%20way%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20has%20time%20and%20again%20been%20mentioned%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20is%20attempted%20to%20be%20flushed%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGuancha%2C%20a%20nationalist%20website%20based%20in%20Shanghai%2C%20follows%20the%20same%20narrative%20as%20those%20pushed%20out%20by%20Huanqiu%20and%20Global%20Times%2C%20and%20paints%20a%20picture%20that%20India's%20partnership%20with%20the%20West%20is%20based%20only%20on%20balancing%20China%20and%20nothing%20more.%20China%20Youth%20Network%2C%20a%20key%20central%20news%20website%20sponsored%20by%20the%20Central%20Committee%20Youth%20League%20of%20China%2C%20while%20saying%20Trudeau%20has%20provided%20no%20evidence%20against%20India%2C%20remarks%20that%20India%20now%20joins%20a%20group%20of%20countries%20known%20for%20assassinating%20political%20opponents%20overseas%2C%20drawing%20a%20comparison%20with%20the%20Jamal%20Khashoggi%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20other%20state%20supported%20Chinese%20websites%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%20which%20raise%20the%20same%20accusations%20against%20India%2C%20without%20evidence%2C%20just%20the%20way%20Trudeau%20has%2C%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20equating%20India%20with%20China.%20They%20seek%20to%20propagate%20the%20narrative%20that%20India%20and%20China%20are%20no%20different%20and%20that%20is%20why%20India%20should%20partner%20with%20China%20rather%20than%20the%20West.%20While%20the%20strife%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20continues%2C%20and%20the%20wait%20for%20any%20evidence%20continues%2C%20the%20possibilities%20of%20a%20rift%20between%20India%20and%20its%20partners%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20is%20cheered%20heartily%20by%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dr.%20Sriparna%20Pathak%20is%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20of%20China%20Studies%2C%20and%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Northeast%20Asian%20Studies%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695632160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fpehqbgjo_justin-trudeau-afp_625x300_22_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fas-canada-messes-up-indo-pacific-strategy-china-has-last-laugh-4421460%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20As%20Canada%20Messes%20Up%20Indo-Pacific%20Strategy%2C%20China%20Has%20Last%20Laugh%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fas-canada-messes-up-indo-pacific-strategy-china-has-last-laugh-4421460%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fas-canada-messes-up-indo-pacific-strategy-china-has-last-laugh-4421460%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fas-canada-messes-up-indo-pacific-strategy-china-has-last-laugh-4421460%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20world's%20largest%20airplane%20was%20destroyed%20by%20Russia%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Ukraine%20estimates%20it%20will%20cost%20%24500%20million%20to%20rebuild.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20what's%20left%20of%20the%20mammoth%20jet.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20An-225%20with%20no%20wings%20or%20cockpit%2C%20taken%20August%2010%20at%20Hostomel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650ddcdde453d50019f7e1ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Antonov%20An-225%20%26quot%3BMriya%26quot%3Bas%20it%20looked%20on%20Aug.%2010%20of%20this%20year.%3Cp%3EIgor%20Lesiv%2Faerovokzal.net%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20world's%20largest%20airplane%20was%20destroyed%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin