%3D%5C%22The%20An-225%20loading%20the%20generator%20in%202009.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650dd9e823ce9d00190897aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221244%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20An-225%20loading%20a%20348%2C000-pound%20generator%20in%202009.%3Cp%3EAntonov%20Company%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nose%20door%20meant%20the%20objects%20could%20slide%20right%20into%20the%20plane%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20load%20and%20unload%20large%20and%20odd-shaped%20freight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.antonov.com%2Fen%2Fairlines%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFleet%2520Antonov%2520Airlines%26amp%3Btext%3DThe%2520AN%252D225%2520was%2520originally%2Centered%2520commercial%2520service%2520in%25202001.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMyria%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20actually%20earned%20itself%20over%20100%20world%20records%20over%20its%20lifetime%2C%20starting%20with%20its%20maiden%20flight%20in%201988%20when%20it%20officially%20became%20the%20heaviest%20and%20largest%20aircraft%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20long-standing%20title%20was%20achieved%20in%202009%20when%20the%20An-225%20set%20the%20record%20for%20airlifting%20the%20heaviest%20piece%20of%20equipment%20ever%20transported%20%E2%80%94%20an%20Alstom%20generator%20stator%20weighing%20174%20tons%20(348%2C000%20pounds)%2C%20which%20could%20only%20be%20flown%20to%20the%20landlocked%20nation%20of%20Armenia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHolding%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20mammoth%20plane%20were%20a%20total%20of%2032%20wheels%20%E2%80%94%2028%20in%20the%20main%20gear%20as%20seven%20rows%20of%20four%2C%20and%20four%20under%20the%20nose.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An-225%20wheels.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F621d074f101faf0019297523%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22723%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETh