f%20new%20connections.%3Cp%3EMargaux%20Duvall%2C%20Lillian%20Lema%2C%20Lynette%20Ban%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EAmericans%20aged%2018%20to%2025%20reported%20feeling%20lonelier%20than%20any%20other%20demographic%20in%20a%20recent%20study.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIn%20search%20of%20connection%2C%20young%20people%20are%20spending%20on%20gym%20memberships%2C%20social%20clubs%2C%20and%20art%20classes.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EInsider%20spoke%20to%2023%20Gen%20Zers.%20Most%20said%20they%20spend%20more%20on%20social%20activities%20than%20pre-pandemic.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELynette%20Ban%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-workers-moved-to-austin-regrets-2023-8%5C%22%3Emoved%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Austin%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20pandemic%20to%20save%20money.%20But%20now%2C%20three%20years%20into%20working%20remotely%2C%20she's%20racked%20up%20a%20new%20expense%3A%20friendships.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBan%20estimates%20she%20spends%20at%20least%20%24500%20a%20month%20on%20various%20memberships%20and%20events%20aimed%20at%20making%20friends%20and%20maintaining%20connections.%20That%20includes%20a%20%242%2C500%20annual%20membership%20to%20the%20social%20club%20Soho%20House%20and%20a%20%24500%20annual%20fee%20for%20the%20gym%20program%20ClassPass.%20That's%20on%20top%20of%20hundreds%20a%20month%20on%20lunches%20and%20dinners%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20prioritizing%2C%20post-pandemic%2C%20more%20of%20these%20clubs%20and%20joining%20these%20organizations%20where%20I%20can%20meet%20new%20people%20and%20build%20a%20network%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Ban%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBan%2C%2026%2C%20is%20like%20many%20young%20Americans%20who%20have%20spent%20an%20important%20chunk%20of%20their%20adult%20lives%20outside%20the%20classrooms%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20other%20shared%20spaces%20where%20offline%20relationships%20are%20so%20often%20formed.%20This%20has%20led%2C%20in%20part%2C%20to%20what%20the%20US%20Surgeon%20General%20Vivek%20Murthy%20has%20called%20an%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fsurgeon-general-social-connection-advisory.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepidemic%20of%20loneliness%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20particularly%20acute%20among%20young%20people.%20Over%20a%20third%20of%20Americans%20aged%2018%20to%2025%20reported%20feeling%20lonely%20frequently%2C%20almost%20all%20the%20time%2C%20or%20all%20the%20time%20in%20the%2030%20days%20preceding%20a%20December%202022%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20Harvard%20Graduate%20School%20of%20Education%20that%20was%20shared%20with%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Weissbourd%2C%20a%20child%20and%20family%20psychologist%20who%20worked%20on%20the%20study%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20people%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2025%20reported%20loneliness%20more%20than%20any%20other%20demographic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20time%20where%20young%20people%20are%20making%20some%20of%20the%20hardest%20and%20most%20difficult%20decisions%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20and%20they%20really%20need%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20Weissbourd%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoneliness%20isn't%20only%20a%20mental-health%20concern.%20Social%20isolation%20can%20be%20as%20dangerous%20as%20smoking%20up%20to%2015%20cigarettes%20a%20day%20and%20contributes%20to%20health%20issues%20including%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20stroke%2C%20and%20dementia%2C%20Murthy%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20interviewed%2023%20young%20adults%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2021%20and%2027%20about%20their%20experiences%20with%20loneliness.%20All%20but%20three%20said%20they're%20spending%20more%20money%20now%20than%20they%20were%20before%20the%20pandemic%20on%20social%20activities%20such%20as%20art%20classes%20and%20gym%20memberships%20to%20make%20friends.%20In%20turn%2C%20many%20said%20that%20they%20are%20spending%20less%20on%20personal%20expenses%20like%20solo%20trips%20or%20TV%20subscriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lynette%20Ban%20(right)%20stands%20with%20her%20friend%20Rachael%20Piotrowski%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65088292f05aa00019be66e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELynette%20Ban%2C%20right%2C%20and%20her%20friend%20Rachael%20went%20to%20a%20pasta-making%20class%20during%20a%20trip%20to%20Italy.%3Cp%3ELynette%20Ban%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoney%20can't%20buy%20Gen%20Zers%20happiness%2C%20but%20they%20do%20hope%20it%20can%20buy%20them%20friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20young%20adults%2C%20especially%20remote%20workers%2C%20are%20trying%20to%20combat%20loneliness%20by%20picking%20up%20new%20hobbies%20and%20activities%20to%20meet%20new%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20having%20that%20social%20experience%20at%20the%20office%20shrinks%20your%20social%20circle%2C%20and%20especially%20when%20you're%20young%2C%20it's%20so%20important%20to%20have%20that%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20Matt%20Schulz%2C%20the%20chief%20credit%20analyst%20for%20LendingTree%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Cabell%2C%2024%2C%20doles%20out%20%2470%20a%20month%20for%20a%20membership%20at%20a%20rock-climbing%20gym%20and%20another%20%24161%20at%20a%20jujitsu%20gym%20in%20Richmond%2C%20Virginia.%20Cabell's%20goal%20with%20both%20memberships%20is%20to%20meet%20new%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20make%20friends%2C%20you%20need%20regularity%2C%20and%20I%20have%20found%20that%20an%20investment%20stake%20is%20a%20good%20way%20to%20elicit%20that%20from%20both%20myself%20and%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Cabell%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20pay%20for%20something%2C%20you'll%20show%20up%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20software%20engineer%20said%20he's%20increased%20his%20investment%20in%20social%20activities%20after%20struggling%20to%20make%20friends%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20types%20of%20activities%20ease%20the%20process%20of%20making%20friends%20more%20so%20than%20free%20activities%20because%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20structured%2C%26quot%3B%20Cabell%20said.%20%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20you're%20stuck%20together%20with%20everyone%20else%20there%20and%20forced%20into%20new%20social%20situations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECabell%20isn't%20alone%20in%20joining%20a%20gym%20to%20make%20friends.%20The%20boutique%20fitness%20franchise%20Orangetheory%20Fitness'%20Gen%20Z%20member%20base%20grew%20200%25%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%202019%20to%20August%201%2C%202023%20%E2%80%94%20faster%20than%20the%20member%20base%20of%20any%20other%20generation%2C%20Ameen%20Kazerouni%2C%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20at%20Orangetheory%20Fitness%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20increased%20focus%20on%20health%20and%20wellness%20and%20the%20strong%20desire%20for%20IRL%20connection%20are%20two%20large%20factors%20that%20are%20driving%20the%20demand%20and%20our%20membership%20growth%20with%20this%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20Lohr%2C%20Orangetheory's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoho%20House%20%E2%80%94%20a%20club%20whose%20stated%20purpose%20is%20for%20%26quot%3Blike-minded%20creative%20thinkers%20to%20meet%2C%20relax%2C%20have%20fun%20and%20grow%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20said%20in%20its%20annual%20earnings%20report%20filed%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fix%3Fdoc%3D%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F0001846510%2F000095017023006592%2Fmcg-20230101.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESEC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%20constitute%20the%20club's%20%26quot%3Bfastest-growing%20cohorts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembership%20to%20Soho%20House's%20New%20York%20flagship%20location%20costs%20about%20%241%2C300%20a%20year%20for%20people%20under%20the%20age%20of%2027.%20A%20membership%20to%20all%20locations%20can%20cost%20as%20much%20as%20%243%2C575%20for%20people%20under%2027%2C%20with%20the%20exact%20price%20dependent%20on%20the%20location%20they%20use%20most%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArt%20studios%20have%20also%20seen%20an%20uptick%20in%20Gen%20Z%20attendees.%20Barley%20Vogel%2C%20the%20owner%20and%20director%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstudioartsdallas.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStudio%20Arts%20Dallas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20there's%20been%20an%20increase%20in%20younger%20adults%20attending%20the%20studio's%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22710%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Art%20Studio%20NY%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650882edcd637c0019c71d6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22532%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYoung%20adults%20have%20been%20attending%20art%20classes%2C%20like%20those%20at%20The%20Art%20Studio%20NY%2C%20in%20order%20%26quot%3Bto%20fulfill%20the%20need%20for%20community.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EThe%20Art%20Studio%20NY%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Schweiger%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theartstudiony.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Art%20Studio%20NY%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20Gen%20Zers%20are%20%26quot%3Battending%20classes%20regularly%20to%20fulfill%20the%20need%20for%20community%20and%20connection.%26quot%3B%20Frequently%2C%20younger%20adults%20are%20coming%20alone%20seeking%20comradery%20in%20addition%20to%20personal%20fulfillment%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20quite%20typical%20for%20students%2C%20adult%20students%2C%20to%20make%20friends%2C%20to%20socialize%20together%2C%20to%20first%20get%20to%20know%20each%20other%20in%20the%20class%20setting%20and%20then%20to%20get%20together%20outside%20of%20classes%2C%26quot%3B%20Schweiger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoureen%20Shallwani%2C%2027%2C%20who%20works%20for%20a%20beauty-tech%20startup%2C%20said%20she%20felt%20like%20she%20had%20to%20restart%20socially%20after%20moving%20from%20Austin%20to%20Philadelphia%20for%20an%20in-person%20job%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShallwani%20joined%20Facebook%20groups%20to%20find%20people%20willing%20to%20see%20movies%20or%20go%20out%20to%20dinner%20with%20her.%20She%20regularly%20attends%20Pilates%20classes%20to%20meet%20people%2C%20and%20saves%20up%20to%20afford%20domestic%20and%20international%20vacations%20with%20friends%20about%20four%20times%20a%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20made%20life%20a%20little%20easier%20to%20be%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20everyone%20feels%20like%20you've%20done%20a%20workout%20together%2C%20everyone%20has%20gone%20through%20an%20experience%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Shallwani%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20talk%20afterwards%2C%20and%20everyone's%20like%2C%20'Should%20we%20get%20drinks%20this%20time%3F'%20or%20'There's%20an%20event%20going%20on%20in%20the%20city%2C%20do%20we%20all%20want%20to%20go%20to%20it%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShallwani%20said%20she's%20been%20anxious%20about%20financial%20stability%2C%20though%20she%20said%20spending%20on%20social%20experiences%20has%20been%20well%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGen%20Zers%20are%20also%20finding%20cheaper%20ways%20to%20solve%20loneliness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Gen%20Zers%20don't%20have%20the%20funds%20%E2%80%94%20or%20the%20will%20%E2%80%94%20to%20spend%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20a%20year%20on%20activities%20and%20memberships%20aimed%20at%20making%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20there%20are%20other%20options.%20Lillian%20Lema%2C%2027%2C%20said%20she%20spent%20a%20Sunday%20in%20August%20eating%20and%20enjoying%20music%20with%20friends%20on%20Peaks%20Island%20in%20Maine.%20The%20social%20gathering%20includ