against%20Pannun%3B%20these%20have%20been%20registered%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Haryana%20and%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurpatwant-singh-pannun-booked-over-khalistan-flags-outside-himachal-assembly-state-borders-sealedhp-ld-2957772%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBanned%20Sikh%20Group's%20Leader%20Charged%20Over%20'Khalistan'%20Flags%20At%20Himachal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20above%2016%20cases%2C%20nine%20are%20under%20the%20stringent%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20according%20to%20the%20dossier%20on%20Pannun.%20Four%20of%20these%20are%20in%20Delhi%2C%20two%20in%20Punjab%20(one%20in%20Amritsar%20and%20another%20in%20Sirhind)%2C%20a%20seventh%20in%20Gurugram%20in%20Haryana%20and%20an%20eighth%20in%20Dharamshala%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ninth%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPannun%20also%20faces%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20other%20cases%20in%20Punjab%20alone%2C%20including%20three%20of%20sedition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EPannun's%20Criminal%20Activities%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20dossier%2C%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20has%20offered%20a%20reward%20of%20US%242.5%20million%20to%20anyone%20who%20could%20hoist%20the%20Khalistani%20flag%20at%20India%20Gate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20reportedly%20also%20offered%20US%241%20million%20to%20any%20police%20personnel%20who%20stopped%20the%20Indian%20flag%20from%20being%20hoisted%20at%20the%20Red%20Fort%20on%20Independence%20Day%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20tried%20several%20times%20to%20get%20Khalistani%20posters%20and%20flags%20installed%20at%20prominent%20places%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3ENIA%20Raids%20On%20Gurpatwant%20Pannun%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast