f%20the%20allegations%20are%20true%2C%20it%20should%20shock%20the%20state's%20conscience%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20ordered%20that%20a%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20be%20appointed%20to%20monitor%20the%20investigation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftripta-tyagi-neha-public-school-muzaffarnagar-i-made-a-mistake-but-theres-no-communal-angle-up-teacher-apologises-4335758%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20a%20seven-year-old%20was%20slapped%20repeatedly%20by%20his%20classmates%20on%20the%20instruction%20of%20their%20teacher%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Muzaffarnagar.%20Calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bserious%20and%20worrying%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20said%20it's%20a%20matter%20of%20right%20to%20life.%20A%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20had%20gone%20viral%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20causing%20massive%20outrage.%20As%20the%20student%20stood%20crying%2C%20his%20classmates%20took%20turns%20to%20slap%20him%2C%20showed%20the%20video.%20The%20teacher%20was%20also%20heard%20in%20the%20video%20asking%20the%20students%20to%20hit%20him%20hard.%20The%20court%C2%A0directed%20the%20UP%20government%20to%20conduct%20counselling%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20and%20other%20students%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20by%20professional%20counsellors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20adjourned%20the%20matter%20for%20October%2030%2C%20and%20directed%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20to%20file%20a%20compliance%20report%20on%20counselling%20of%20students%20involved%2C%20and%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20education%20of%20the%20victim%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20recorded%20serious%20objections%20to%20the%20content%20of%20the%20FIR%2C%20which%20does%20not%20have%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20the%20father%20of%20the%20child.%20The%20father%20had%20given%20a%20statement%20that%20his%20son%20was%20beaten%20because%20of%20his%20religion%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20cour