x-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25113020%2FSEM2.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25113020%2FSEM2.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25113020%2FSEM2-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25113020%2FSEM2-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674676%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Shahi%20Eidgah%20Masjid%20and%20the%20Shri%20Krishna%20Janmasthan%20temple%20in%20Mathura.%20Photo%3A%20Tarushi%20Aswani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuslim-%3Cem%3Emukt%3C%2Fem%3E%20Mathura%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENizamuddin%20Azeem%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20streets%20leading%20to%20the%20Eidgah.%20The%20three-domed%20structure%20holds%20heaps%20of%20memories%20from%20his%20childhood%20Eids.%20Now%2C%20Azeem%20says%2C%20there%20is%20a%20stillness%20near%20the%20structure.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20hesitate%20to%20spend%20much%20time%20here%2C%20they%20just%20pray%20and%20leave%2C%20as%20if%20something%20ominous%20will%20happen%20if%20they%20stay%20longer.%20This%20has%20happened%20since%20they%20claimed%20that%20the%20Eidgah%20is%20built%20on%20temple%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20Azeem%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMehraj%20Alam%2C%20a%20BAMCEF%20(Backward%20and%20Minority%20Communities%20Employees%20Federation)%20worker%2C%20said%20that%20the%20whole%20controversy%20around%20the%20Eidgah%20was%20only%20to%20have%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Muslim-mukt%20Mathura%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Muslim-free%20Mathura)%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CSuddenly%20they%20have%20problems%20with%20the%20place%20where%20Muslims%20pray%2C%20the%20food%20Muslims%20sell%20and%20consume.%20They%20are%20even%20using%20the%20law%20to%20favour%20their%20own%20narrative%20of%20what%20existed%20before%20which%20structure%2C%20to%20only%20martyr%20another%20mosque%20after%20Babri%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20stands%20out%20here%2C%20when%20one%20tries%20to%20understand%20the%20dispute%2C%20is%20the%20disturbing%20deployment%20of%20law%20to%20discern%20the%20true%20custodians%20of%20the%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Janmabhoomi%20Trust%20in%20Agra%20is%20challenging%20a%20compromise%20made%20in%20the%201960s%20between%20a%20temple%20body%20and%20the%20Shahi%20Masjid%20Eidgah%20over%20disputed%20land.%20The%20trust%20is%20claiming%20a%2013.37-acre%20tract%20of%20land%20next%20to%20to%20the%20Sri%20Krishna%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%20complex.%20Several%20suits%20have%20been%20filed%20saying%20that%20the%20Eidgah%20complex%20was%20built%20on%20land%20belonging%20to%20the%20Janmasthan%20Trust.%20The%20trust%20is%20now%20seeking%20a%20cancellation%20of%20the%20agreement%20made%20in%201968%20and%20a%20declaration%20that%20the%20land%20solely%20belongs%20to%20the%20Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98Scared%20to%20Buy%2C%20Eat%20Meat%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslims%20in%20Mathura%20After%20Arrests%20on%20Suspicion%20of%20Cow%20Slaughter%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fscared-to-buy-eat-meat-muslims-in-mathura-after-arrests-on-suspicion-of-cow-slaughter%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Scared%20to%20Buy%2C%20Eat%20Meat%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslims%20in%20Mathura%20After%20Arrests%20on%20Suspicion%20of%20Cow%20Slaughter%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellation%20that%20the%20trust%20is%20seeking%20is%20based%20on%20an%20agreement%20undertaken%20by%20the%20Sri%20Krishna%20Janmabhoomi%20Seva%20Sangh%2C%20a%20body%20of%20the%20temple%20that%20was%20dissolved%20later.%20This%20agreement%20approved%20the%20passover%20of%20the%20contentious%20portion%20of%20land%20to%20the%20Eidgah%20committee%20in%201968.%20In%20its%20petition%2C%20the%20Trust%20has%20said%20that%20the%20deal%2C%20which%20was%20finalised%20before%20the%20civil%20judge%20(senior%20division)%2C%20Mathura%20in%201973-74%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20binding%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20temple%20as%20the%20Seva%20Sangh%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20authority%E2%80%9D%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Mohammed%20Iqbal%2C%20who%20represents%20the%20Shahi%20Eidgah%20committee%20in%20the%20case%2C%20believes%20that%20while%20no%20one%20had%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20coexistence%20of%20the%20structures%20for%20years%20together%2C%20problems%20have%20emerged%20after%20the%20politicisation%20of%20religious%20structures%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fayodhya-verdict-supreme-court-full-text%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20title%20dispute%20verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20delivered.%20The%20Mathura%20mosque%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fshri-krishna-janmabhoomi-mathura-shahi-idgah-mosque-temple-supreme-court%5C%22%3Ethird%C2%A0after%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20in%20Varanasi%20that%20Hindutva%20organisations%20have%20claimed%20is%20illegal.%20Iqbal%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20(Special%20Provisions)%20Act%2C%201991%20was%20being%20sidelined%20in%20this%20matter.%20The%20Act%20says%20that%20a%20mosque%2C%20temple%2C%20church%20or%20any%20place%20of%20public%20worship%20in%20existence%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947%20will%20retain%20the%20same%20religious%20character%20that%20it%20had%20on%20that%20day%20%E2%80%93%20irrespective%20of%20its%20history%20%E2%80%93%20and%20cannot%20be%20changed%20by%20the%20courts%20or%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fplaces-of-worship-act-ashwini-kumar-supreme-court-ayodhya%5C%22%3EPlaces%20of%20Worship%20Act%3A%20Is%20Supreme%20Court%20Unwittingly%20Helping%20Centre%20With%20Proxy%20Litigation%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Ready%20to%20retaliate%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Burhanuddin%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Eidgah%20committee%2C%20views%20the%20case%20against%20the%20Eidgah%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20Hinduise%20Mathura%20more%20than%20the%20existing%20bans%20would%20ever%20be%20able%20to.%20%E2%80%9CMathura%20has%20mandirs%20and%20masjids.%20We%20respect%20that%20Hindus%20from%20across%20India%20come%20here%20for%20their%20religious%20purpose%2C%20but%20Mathura%20is%20ours%20too%2C%20we%20have%20lived%20along%20Hindus%20peacefully%20for%20centuries.%20Why%20is%20our%20existence%20being%20made%20into%20a%20court%20case%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20Muslims%20in%20the%20holy%20Hindu%20city%2C%20Burhanuddin%20questions%20the%20state%20and%20its%20decisions%20regarding%20Muslims%20every%20day.%20From%20the%20ban%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20meat%20to%20abrupt%20demolitions%20of%20Muslim%20homes%2C%20to%20their%20place%20of%20worship%20falling%20prey%20to%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20Muslims%20in%20Mathura%20have%20a%20plethora%20of%20problems%20that%20surround%20their%20existence%20as%20a%20non-Hindu%20community%20in%20a%20territory%20holy%20to%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20these%20questions%2C%20Vijay%20Bahadur%20Singh%2C%20public%20relations%20officer%2C%20Shri%20Krishna%20Janmasthan%20Temple%2C%20feels%20that%20Mathura%E2%80%99s%20glory%20will%20finally%20be%20restored%20once%20the%20%E2%80%98battle%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20Janmasthan%20is%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'They%20Bulldozed%20Our%20Life'%3A%20Mathura's%20Muslims%20Struggle%20as%20the%20State%20Crushes%20Their%20Homes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthey-bulldozed-our-life-mathuras-muslims-struggle-as-the-state-crushes-their-homes%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98They%20Bulldozed%20Our%20Life%E2%80%99%3A%20Mathura%E2%80%99s%20Muslims%20Struggle%20as%20the%20State%20Crushes%20Their%20Homes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Trust%20has%20demanded%20that%20the%20mosque%2C%20which%20abuts%20the%20temple%2C%20be%20removed%20and%20the%20land%20returned%20to%20the%20Trust%2C%20Singh%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20mosque%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20%E2%80%98structure%E2%80%99%20that%20has%20been%20illegally%20used%20by%20Muslims%20for%20decades%20to%20offers%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESanatan%20dharma%3C%2Fem%3E%20teaches%20us%20to%20pick%20up%20arms%20for%20religion%2C%20and%20we%20have%20no%20problem%20in%20that%2C%20but%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20take%20this%20step.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20added%20that%20at%20any%20point%2C%20Hindus%20would%20not%20hesitate%20to%20retaliate%20if%20the%20situation%20called%20for%20it.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20if%20Muslims%20were%20keen%20to%20follow%20a%20rigid%20form%20of%20Islam%2C%20they%20are%20free%20to%20leave%20Mathura%20and%20practice%20it%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMandirs%20are%20no%20more%20a%20sign%20of%20amity%20for%20Mathura%E2%80%99s%20Muslims%20%E2%80%93%20instead%2C%20they%20are%20a%20symbolic%20reminder%20that%20their%20lives%20and%20livelihoods%20are%20being%20flattened%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Hinduism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETarushi%20Aswani%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695625218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25112937%2FSEM1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmathura-muslims-shahi-eidgah-krishna-janmasthan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ever%20since%20the%20verdict%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20title%20dispute%20case%2C%20Muslims%20in%20Mathura%20believe%20the%20politicisation%20of%20religious%20structures%20has%20left%20them%20in%20an%20even%20more%20precarious%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmathura-muslims-shahi-eidgah-krishna-janmasthan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Addictive%20medicine%2C%20overdose%20deaths%20add%20to%20Punjab's%20miseries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695624926000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103926962%2Cimgsize-28274.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Fpunjabs-vicious-cycle-addictive-medicine-overdose-deaths-add-to-states-miseries%2Farticleshow%2F103924525.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20has%20made%20a%20commitment%20to%20make%20Punjab%20a%20drug-free%20state%20by%20next%20Independence%20Day%2C%20but%20the%20ground%20reality%20is%20different.%20Despite%20%E2%80%9Cbest%20efforts%E2%80%9D%20put%20in%20by%20various%20state%20government%20wings%20since%20the%20constitution%20of%20the%20anti-drug%20special%20task%20force%20(STF)%20during%20the%20Congress%20regime%20in%20April%202017%2C%20the%20state%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20achieve%20desirable%20results%20in%20containing%20substance%20abuse%20and%20drug%20overdose%20deaths.%E2%80%8B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SANJEEV%20VERMA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Fpunjabs-vicious-cycle-addictive-medicine-overdose-deaths-add-to-states-miseries%2Farticleshow%2F103924525.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Skill%20Development%20Case%3A%20SC%20Refuses%20Urgent%20Mentioning%20of%20Naidu's%20Petition%20to%20Quash%20FIR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24143246%2Fnaidu.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20refused%20urgent%20mentioning%20of%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20to%20quash%20the%20case%20registered%20against%20him%20in%20an%20alleged%20skill%20development%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fcome-tomorrow-supreme-court-refuses-to-take-up-chandrababu-naidus-plea-to-quash-fir-today-238599%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20petition%20was%20not%20included%20in%20the%20list%20of%20oral%20mentions%20for%20Monday.%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20refused%20out-of-turn%20listing%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20asking%C2%A0Naidu%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Siddharth%20Luthra%20to%20mention%20it%20again%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENaidu%20had%20filed%20a%20special%20leave%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Saturday%20challenging%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20dismissal%20of%20his%20plea%20to%20quash%20the%20FIR.%20Subsequntly%2C%20a%20court%20in%20Vijayawada%20granted%20two%20days%E2%80%99%20police%20custody%20to%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Crime%20Investigation%20Department%20(CID)%20to%20interrogate%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20with%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20custody%20set%20to%20end%2C%20the%20Vijayawada%20ACB%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fchandrababu-naidus-judicial-custody-extended-till-oct-5%5C%22%3Eextended%20it%20by%2011%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20until%20October%205.%20The%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20chief%20was%20produced%20before%20the%20court%20virtually%20from%20the%20Rajahmundry%20Central%20Jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnaidus-arrest-what-is-the-andhra-pradesh-skill-development-scam%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20on%20September%209%2C%C2%A0as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR%20registered%20by%20the%20AP%20CID%20in%202021%20over%20an%20alleged%20multi-crore%20scam%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20State%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20term%20(2014-19)%2C%20the%20state%20government%20and%20two%20companies%20initiated%20a%20project%20to%20create%20six%20centres%20of%20excellence%20(CoE)%20and%2036%20technical%20skill%20development%20institutes.%20The%20estimated%20cost%20was%20around%20Rs%203%2C281%20crore%2C%20which%20the%20CID%20claims%20is%20an%20inflated%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CID%20claims%20that%20Naidu%20and%20others%20allegedly%20routed%20hawala%20transactions%20through%20a%20network%20of%20shell%20companies%2C%20did%20not%20adhere%20to%20procedures%20and%20disregarded%20observations%20regarding%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20viability.%20The%20TDP%20has%20set%20up%20a%20website%20to%20counter%20the%20allegations%2C%20highlighting%20that%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20established%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20numbers%20of%20clusters%20and%20trained%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20candidates%20among%20all%20the%20states%20that%20had%20similar%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20high%20court%20had%20dismissed%20Nadiu%E2%80%99s%20petition%20to%20quash%20the%20case%20while%20noting%20that%20the%20investigation%20is%20attaining%20finality%20and%20the%20court%20cannot%20interfere%20at%20this%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENaidu%E2%80%99s%20arguments%20in%20SC%20petition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20petition%20in%20the%20top%20court%20says%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Csuddenly%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%E2%80%9D%20and%20arrested%20in%20an%20illegal%20manner%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20reasons%E2%80%9D.%20While%20claiming%20that%20due%20process%20was%20not%20followed%20before%20his%20arrest%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20seeking%20mandatory%20approval%20under%20Section%2017-A%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%2C%201988%2C%20the%20plea%20states%20that%20the%20FIR%20is%20a%20case%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20vendetta%E2%80%9D.%20Naidu%20and%20his%20family%20%E2%80%9Care%20being%20targeted%20to%20crush%20all%20opposition%20to%20the%20party%20in%20power%20in%20the%20Respondent%20State%20with%20elections%20coming%20near%20in%202024%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20petition%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20also%20accused%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20CID%20of%20acting%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20damage%20the%20TDP%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20election%2C%20which%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20parallel%20to%20the%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CID%20is%20threatening%20the%20officers%20and%20others%20to%20implicate%20the%20Petitioner%2C%20his%20family%20and%20the%20Party.%20The%20continuing%20political%20vendetta%20by%20the%20State%20Administration%20is%20demonstrated%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20various%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20Petitioner%E2%80%99s%20party%20have%20in%20the%20past%20been%20arrested%20and%20now%20hastily%20are%20being%20sought%20to%20be%20implicated%20in%20false%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petition%20says%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695624909000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24143246%2Fnaidu.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fskill-development-case-sc-refuses-urgent-mentioning-naidu-petition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20separate%20development%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Vijayawada%20ACB%20court%20extended%20the%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister's%20police%20custody%20by%2011%20days%2C%20until%20October%205.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fskill-development-case-sc-refuses-urgent-mentioning-naidu-petition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Is%20The%20Place%20With%20The%20Cleanest%20Air%20On%20Earth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20for%20clean%20air%20on%20Earth%20has%20become%20an%20increasingly%20urgent%20and%20global%20endeavour%20in%20recent%20years.%20As%20the%20world%20grapples%20with%20the%20devastating%20impacts%20of%20air%20pollution%20and%20climate%20change%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20recognition%20of%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20clean%2C%20breathable%20air%20for%20the%20health%20and%20well-being%20of%20all%20living%20beings.%20And%20one%20place%20stands%20out%20in%20this%20respect%2C%20offering%20the%20cleanest%20air%20to%20visitors.%20Called%20Cape%20Grim%2C%20the%20peninsula%20is%20near%20the%20north-western%20tip%20of%20Tasmania%2C%20near%20Australia%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20major%20reason%20for%20this%20unique%20experience%20is%20the%20land%20patch's%20remoteness.%20Few%20travellers%20make%20it%20to%20Cape%20Grim%2C%20which%20is%20popularly%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BEdge%20of%20the%20World%26quot%3B.%20And%20a%20station%20measuring%20the%20air%20quality%20shows%20it%20has%20the%20cleanest%20air%20on%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20strong%20westerly%20winds%20that%20buffet%20the%20Cape%20Grim%20air%20monitoring%20station%20have%20travelled%20thousands%20of%20kilometres%20over%20the%20icy%20Southern%20Ocean%2C%20making%20air%20measured%20here%20some%20of%20the%20cleanest%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Ann%20Stavert%2C%20senior%20research%20scientist%20at%20the%20Commonwealth%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20Organisation%20(CSIRO)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ftravel%2Farticle%2F20230918-a-picturesque-island-with-the-cleanest-air-on-earth%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20region%20is%20famous%20for%20ferocious%20gusts%2C%20which%20can%20reach%20up%20to%20180%20kmph%20and%20carry%20unspoiled%20air%20from%20Antarctica.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20wind%20speed%20and%20wind%20direction%20data%20we%20know%20that%20about%2030%25%20of%20the%20air%20reaching%20Cape%20Grim%20can%20be%20considered%20what%20scientists%20call%20%26quot%3Bbaseline%26quot%3B.%20That%20is%2C%20air%20that%20is%20not%20influenced%20by%20local%20atmospheric%20sources%20and%20sinks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Stavert.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20remote%20clean%20air%20sites%20around%20the%20world%20include%20Mauna%20Loa%20station%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20Macquarie%20Island%2C%20Casey%20Station%20in%20Antarctica%20and%20the%20Svalbard%20town%20of%20Ny-Alesund.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EScientists%2C%20policymakers%2C%20and%20activists%20around%20the%20world%20are%20working%20tirelessly%20to%20monitor%20air%20quality%2C%20reduce%20emissions%20from%20industrial%20and%20transportation%20sources%2C%20and%20promote%20sustainable%20practices%20that%20protect%20our%20planet's%20fragile%20atmosphere.%20This%20quest%20for%20clean%20air%20is%20not%20only%20about%20preserving%20the%20environment%20but%20also%20about%20safeguarding%20human%20health%20and%20ensuring%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20regard%2C%20Cape%20Grim%20comes%20as%20a%20fresh%20breath%20of%20air%20that%20can%20help%20people%20from%20across%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20the%20marketers.%20They%20are%20selling%20bottled%20Tasmanian%20air%20to%20provide%20people%20in%20polluted%20places%20around%20the%20world%20with%20a%20healthy%20blast%20of%20unsullied%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said%20there's%20around%20130%20inhalations%20of%20fresh%20Tasmanian%20air%20per%20canister.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695624600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Flk132gi_cape-grim-tasmania-afp-1200_625