avour%20and%20only%20two%20votes%20against%20it%20on%20Day%203%20of%20the%20five-day%20special%20session%20of%20Parliament%20last%20week%20before%20receiving%20unanimous%20support%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20PM%20Modi%20last%20week%2C%20Ms%20Bharti%20demanded%20that%2050%25%20of%20the%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20legislative%20bodies%20be%20reserved%20for%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20including%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%20and%20OBCs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20afraid%20of%20the%20outcome%2C%20but%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20the%20constitutional%20amendment%20to%20be%20implemented%20without%20the%20OBC%20quota%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Bharti%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20letter%20to%20the%20PM%2C%20Ms%20Bharti%20pointed%20out%20that%20backward%20caste%20women%20in%20Panchayati%20Raj%20and%20local%20bodies%20already%20have%20special%20reservations%2C%20and%20she%20argued%20that%20backward%20Muslim%20women%2C%20as%20recognised%20by%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%2C%20should%20also%20be%20considered%20for%20reservations%20in%20legislative%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20has%20gone%20against%20a%20key%20party%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20expressing%20her%20disappointment%20at%20not%20being%20invited%20to%20her%20party's%20Jan%20Ashirwad%20Yatrain%20the%20state%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Ms%20Bharti%20announced%20that%20she%20would%20not%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20yatra%20even%20if%20she%20received%20an%20invitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Bharti%20kicked%20off%20a%20storm%20within%20the%20party%20after%20suggesting%20that%20BJP%20leaders%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bnervous%26quot%3B%20if%20she%20was%20present%20during%20the%20yatra%20as%20all%20the%20attention%20would%20be%20on%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20titan%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20politics%2C%20in%202003%2C%20she%20led%20the%20BJP%20to%20a%20landslide%20victory%2C%20ending%20the%2010-year%20rule%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20headed%20by%20Digvijaya%20Singh.%20However%2C%20she%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20BJP%20in%202005%20for%20indiscipline%20and%20reinstated%20only%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20criticism%20of%20the%20state%20BJP%20unit%2C%20Ms%20Bharti%20said%20that%20she%20will%20continue%20her%20bond%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20and%20campaign%20for%20the%20party%20as%20and%20when%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695622020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-07%2Ffnebk2uo_uma-bharti_625x300_20_July_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuma-bharti-womens-reservation-bill-ahead-of-pms-bhopal-visit-uma-bhartis-quota-pitch-for-obc-women-4420975%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20mega%20BJP%20workers%20meet%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Bhopal%20today%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20senior%20party%20leader%20Uma%20Bharti%20said%20the%20recently-cleared%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20should%20not%20be%20implemented%20without%20OBC%20quota.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuma-bharti-womens-reservation-bill-ahead-of-pms-bhopal-visit-uma-bhartis-quota-pitch-for-obc-women-4420975%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuma-bharti-womens-reservation-bill-ahead-of-pms-bhopal-visit-uma-bhartis-quota-pitch-for-obc-women-4420975%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuma-bharti-womens-reservation-bill-ahead-of-pms-bhopal-visit-uma-bhartis-quota-pitch-for-obc-women-4420975%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Police%20identify%20woman's%20body%20found%20in%20alligator's%20mouth%22%2C%2