rong%3EDeposit%20Process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERBI%20stated%20that%20individuals%20can%20deposit%20Rs%202%2C000%20notes%20at%20their%20respective%20banks%20without%20any%20specific%20limit.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20usual%20KYC%20(Know%20Your%20Customer)%20requirements%20and%20other%20legal%20deposit%20norms%20will%20still%20be%20applicable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFor%20those%20using%20a%20BSBD%20(Basic%20Savings%20Bank%20Deposit)%20or%20Jan%20Dhan%20account%2C%20the%20regular%20deposit%20limits%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20in%20effect.%20This%20means%20that%20if%20you%20wish%20to%20deposit%20Rs%202000%20notes%20exceeding%20a%20certain%20amount%20in%20these%20accounts%2C%20you%20will%20need%20to%20adhere%20to%20the%20prescribed%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFurthermore%2C%20in%20accordance%20with%20Rule%20114B%20of%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Rules%2C%20individuals%20must%20provide%20their%20PAN%20(Permanent%20Account%20Number)%20when%20making%20cash%20deposits%20exceeding%20Rs%2050%2C000%20in%20a%20single%20day%20at%20either%20a%20bank%20or%20post%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EExchage%20Process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EUntil%20September%2030%2C%20individuals%20also%20have%20the%20facility%20to%20exchange%20Rs%202000%20notes%20at%2019%20Regional%20Offices%20(ROs)%20of%20the%20RBI.%20Besides%20that%2C%20one%20can%20also%20exchange%20Rs%202000%20banknotes%20at%20any%20nearby%20bank%20branch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20RBI's%20guidelines%20are%20straightforward%3A%20As%20these%20notes%20are%20legal%20tender%2C%20the%20exchange%20should%20be%20done%20without%20the%20requirement%20of%20a%20request%20slip%20or%20ID%20proof.%20However%2C%20some%20public%20sector%20banks%20have%20implemented%20a%20different%20approach.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20advisable%20to%20have%20an%20ID%20proof%20handy%20when%20exchanging%20this%20currency%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBank%20Holidays%20This%20Week%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E-Banks%20will%20be%20open%20from%20Monday%20to%20Wednesday%20(September%2025%20to%20September%2027).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E-Thursday%2C%20September%2028%2C%20will%20be%20a%20holiday%20in%20observance%20of%20Milad-un-Nabi%20or%20Id-e-Milad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E-Banks%20will%20resume%20regular%20working%20hours%20on%20Friday%20and%20Saturday%20(September%2029%20and%20September%2030).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20means%20that%20you%20can%20exchange%20or%20deposit%20your%20Rs%202000%20notes%20from%20September%2025%20to%20September%2027%20and%20then%20again%20on%20September%2029%20and%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695621780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F82dsbq6g_rs-2000-note-ani-_625x300_23_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-2-000-note-exchange-or-deposit-deadline-ends-in-5-days-september-30-heres-what-you-can-do-4420794%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India's%20%26quot%3Bclean%20note%20policy%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20highest%20denomination%20currency%20note%20in%20India%20-%20Rs%202%2C000%20note%2C%20will%20lose%20its%20status%20as%20legal%20tender%20after%20September%2030%2C%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-2-000-note-exchange-or-deposit-deadline-ends-in-5-days-september-30-heres-what-you-can-do-4420794%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-2-000-note-exchange-or-deposit-deadline-ends-in-5-days-september-30-heres-what-you-can-do-4420794%2Famp%2F1%22%2