n%E2%80%99%20proposal%20and%20politics%20in%20the%20north-east%20at%20an%20hourlong%20discussion%20organised%20by%20the%20Pratidin%20Media%20Network.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20are%20five%20key%20takeaways%20from%20the%20discussion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpcoming%20assembly%20elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20appeared%20fairly%20confident%20about%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20victory%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20say%20right%20now%20we%E2%80%99re%20probably%20winning%20Telangana%20%E2%80%A6%20we%20are%20certainly%20winning%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20We%20are%20certainly%20winning%20Rajasthan%2C%20we%20are%20very%20close%20and%20we%20think%20we%E2%80%99ll%20be%20able%20to%20win.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20key%20learning%20from%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20polls%2C%20which%20the%20Congress%20won%2C%20was%20to%20have%20its%20own%20narrative%20rather%20than%20reacting%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdistractions%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20BJP.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20try%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20Telangana%20election%2C%20we%20are%20controlling%20the%20narrative.%20The%20BJP%20is%20not%20even%20in%20the%20narrative.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20%5BBJP%5D%20has%20been%20decimated.%20It%E2%80%99s%20over%20in%20in%20Telangana%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20narrative%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20we%20are%20controlling%20the%20narrative.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20the%20narrative%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20we%20are%20controlling%20the%20narrative%3B%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20BJP%20tries%20to%20do%2C%20they%20are%20not%20capturing%20the%20narrative%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20he%20claimed%20the%20people%20are%20happy%20with%20the%20Congress%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20social%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20the%20work%20done%20in%20the%20area%20of%20healthcare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDifferences%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20accepted%20that%20there%20were%20some%20fundamental%20differences%20between%20various%20parties%20that%20have%20come%20together%20under%20the%20umbrella%20called%20INDIA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20%5Bthe%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20parties%5D%20can%20sit%20down%20and%20say%20%5Bto%20each%20other%5D%20that%20%E2%80%98we%20don%E2%80%99t%20agree%20with%20you%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20there%20is%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20flexibility.%20And%20I%20am%20quite%20happy%20with%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20all%20opposition%20parties%20understand%20what%20is%20at%20stake%20now%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20idea%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20fighting%20to%20defend%20that%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20nation%2C%20one%20election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20labelled%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthreat-to-federalism-opposition-criticises-centres-unilateral-one-nation-one-election-call%5C%22%3Esimultaneously%20conduct%20national%20and%20state%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20yet%20another%20distraction%20and%20nothing%20else.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20the%20idea%20was%20thrown%20into%20public%20discourse%20by%20the%20BJP%20when%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20leading%20media%20outlets%20had%20come%20out%20with%20fresh%20exposes%20on%20Gautam%20Adani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fkaran-thapar-interview-sebi-former-chairman-damodaran-adani-financial-times%5C%22%3EFormer%20SEBI%20Chief%20Says%20Adani%20Story%20by%20FT-OCCRP%20%E2%80%98Very%20Persuasive%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20these%20distractions%20are%20floated%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20avoid%20discourse%20on%20pressing%20issues%20like%20unemployment%2C%20huge%20inequality%2C%20the%20concentration%20of%20wealth%20and%20atrocities%20against%20tribal%20people.%20He%20said%20the%20apparent%20bid%20to%20change%20the%20name%20of%20the%20country%20was%20another%20distraction%20and%20added%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20not%20pay%20heed%20to%20these%20distractions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20census%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20reiterated%20that%20a%20caste%20census%20was%20the%20urgent%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20He%20said%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20the%20party%20would%20do%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20is%20to%20release%20the%20data%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fcongress-chief-kharge-writes-to-pm-modi-demanding-caste-census-news-279032%5C%22%3Esurvey%20done%20by%20the%20UPA%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20record%20the%20socio-economic%20characteristics%20of%20and%20castes%20in%2025%20crore%20Indian%20households.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20even%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20has%20that%20survey%E2%80%99s%20(caste)%20data%2C%20which%20it%20was%20not%20releasing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20of%20the%20near-unanimous%20support%20in%20parliament%20for%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20so%20there%20is%20no%20scope%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20delay%20its%20implementation%20if%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3EAll%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20to%20say%20that%2033%25%20seats%20are%20going%20to%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20reiterating%20his%20demand%20in%20parliament%20for%20a%20quota%20for%20OBC%20women%20within%20the%20overall%20women%E2%80%99s%20quota.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20in%20the%20Northeast%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20ruled%20out%20any%20alliance%20with%20the%20All%20India%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20(AIUDF)%20party%20in%20Assam.%20Led%20by%20Maulana%20Badruddin%20Ajmal%2C%20the%20AIUDF%20is%20considered%20a%20minority-based%20party.%20The%20Congress%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fassam-congress-snaps-ties-with-aiudf%2Farticle36196087.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esnapped%20its%20ties%20with%20the%20AIUDF%20in%202021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20owing%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbaffling%20behaviour%20and%20attitude%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20party%20%E2%80%9Cin%20relation%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20expressed%20grave%20concerns%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20and%20said%20what%20he%20saw%20there%20was%20something%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20seen%20in%20his%20entire%20political%20life%2C%20recalling%20an%20incident%20where%20a%20security%20staffer%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20was%20advised%20to%20leave%20his%20contingent%20when%20visiting%20a%20Meitei-dominated%20area%2C%20and%20vice-versa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20did%20not%20rule%20out%20another%20episode%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20from%20the%20western%20part%20of%20India%20to%20its%20east.%20He%20said%20the%20%3Cem%3Eyatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir%20was%20a%20learning%20experience%20for%20him%20and%20that%20he%20may%20want%20to%20do%20it%20from%20west%20to%20east%20also.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20he%20did%20not%20commit%20to%20any%20specific%20plans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695576145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24213716%2FRaGa-at-Pratidin.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-says-he-is-confident-of-cong-victory-in-assembly-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20leader%20ruled%20out%20any%20alliance%20with%20the%20Assam-based%20AIUDF%20and%20said%20he%20would%20want%20to%20have%20another%20version%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20from%20the%20western%20part%20of%20India%20to%20its%20east.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-says-he-is-confident-of-cong-victory-in-assembly-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Biden%20administration%20is%20poised%20to%20allow%20Israeli%20citizens%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20US%20without%20a%20US%20visa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695576035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103913165%2Cimgsize-31496.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fthe-biden-administration-is-poised-to-allow-israeli-citizens-to-travel-to-the-us-without-a-us-visa%2Farticleshow%2F103913075.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103913075.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20is%20poised%20to%20admit%20Israel%20this%20week%20into%20an%20exclusive%20club%20that%20will%20allow%20its%20citizens%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20United%20States%20without%20a%20US%20visa%20despite%20Washington's%20ongoing%20concerns%20abo