%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23101923%2FIMG_2534-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20been%20some%20time%20since%20the%20horrific%20incident%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fvideos%2Ftoi-original%2Fup-accused-who-pulled-girls-dupatta-and-ran-over-their-bike-on-her-shot-at-by-police%2Fvideoshow%2F103756057.cms%5C%22%3Ea%2015-year-old%20girl%20died%20because%20two%20men%20passing%20by%20pulled%20her%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fvideos%2Ftoi-original%2Fup-accused-who-pulled-girls-dupatta-and-ran-over-their-bike-on-her-shot-at-by-police%2Fvideoshow%2F103756057.cms%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edupatta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(stole)%2C%20making%20her%20fall.%20A%20passing%20motorbike%20ran%20into%20her%2C%20killing%20her%20immediately.%20To%20be%20noted%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20that%20she%20was%20harassed%20and%20died%20that%20made%20the%20news%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20because%20those%20guys%20tried%20to%20snatch%20arms%20from%20the%20policemen%20nearby%20and%20tried%20to%20run%2C%20eventually%20getting%20shot%20in%20the%20legs%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20woman%20in%20north%20India%20would%20have%20been%20stunned%20by%20the%20news.%20Angry%2C%20yes.%20Surprised%2C%20no.%20We%20have%20all%20grown%20up%20with%20several%20incidents%20like%20this%20%E2%80%93%20mostly%20being%20%E2%80%98lucky%E2%80%99%20with%20just%20falling%2C%20scratching%20our%20knees%2C%20elbows%2C%20injuries%20to%20forehead%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20badly%20you%20fell%20and%20where%20you%20knocked%20yourself.%20When%20I%20read%20the%20news%2C%20there%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20incident%20that%20cropped%20up%2C%20there%20were%20way%20too%20many%20and%20the%20anger%20didn%E2%80%99t%20subside.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20well%20known%20reasons%20for%20patriarchy%20behind%20street%20harassment%20and%20violence%2C%20especially%20in%20north%20India.%20Lots%20of%20conversations%20on%20dress%20code%20for%20women%20%E2%80%93%20mostly%20why%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20wear%20western%20clothes.%20Yet%2C%20I%20have%20always%20found%20a%20severe%20lack%20of%20conversation%20on%20the%20imposition%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esalwar-kameez%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20dupatta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Indian%20long%20shirt%2C%20loose%20trousers%20and%20stole)%20imposed%20on%20young%20girls%20and%20women%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20turn%2012%20or%2013%2C%20and%20how%20utterly%20sexualised%20it%20is.%20Patriarchy%20starts%20from%20homes%2C%20not%20the%20streets%3B%20and%20the%20role%20of%20parents%2C%20especially%20mothers%2C%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%20The%20way%20they%20impose%20%E2%80%98new%20clothes%E2%80%99%20on%20their%20daughters%2C%20and%20never%20have%20a%20conversation%20with%20their%20sons%20about%20respecting%20women%20or%20even%20their%20own%20sisters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20did%20my%20basic%20schooling%20in%20Karnal%2C%20Haryana%20because%20my%20parents%20taught%20at%20a%20college%20and%20school%20there.%20Even%20though%20Karnal%20is%20a%20town%20with%20a%20huge%20migrant%20population%20%E2%80%93%201947%20and%201984%20Punjabi%20refugees%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Jat%20culture%20still%20rules.%20Punjabis%20have%20a%20similar%20cultural%20background%20so%20in%20spite%20of%20land%20and%20resources-%20related%20animosity%2C%20they%20gel%20well%20together%20culturally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Flaws-sexual-violence-brij-bhushan-saakhi%5C%22%3ELaws%20Alone%20Cannot%20Prevent%20Sexual%20Violence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20my%20classmates%20were%20Jats%20or%20Punjabis%2C%20we%20were%20the%20outsiders.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20conform%20to%20local%20standards%20and%20my%20parents%20were%20progressive%20enough%20to%20not%20dictate%20what%20I%20wear.%20However%2C%20a%20much%20bigger%20reason%20why%20I%20absolutely%20stayed%20away%20from%20salwar%20kameez%20and%20dupatta%20(or%20suit%20as%20is%20popularly%20known%20in%20the%20Haryana-Punjab%20region)%20while%20growing%20up%20was%20because%20I%20saw%20how%20it%20immediately%20sexualised%20the%20bodies%20of%20my%20friends%20and%20classmates%20and%20how%20street%20harassment%20exponentially%20increased%20once%20you%20started%20wearing%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20like%20a%20clear%20signal%20to%20the%20world%20that%20this%20girl%20has%20grown%20up%20and%20is%20now%20available%20for%20harassment.%20The%20dirty%20gaze%20of%20middle-aged%20and%20older%20men%20at%20school%20going%20girls%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20something%20I%20missed.%20Yet%2C%20they%20would%20return%20home%20to%20cover%20their%20daughters%20%E2%80%93%20or%20because%20of%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20growing-up%20body%20was%20a%20dirty%20thing%20to%20be%20covered%20in%20as%20many%20layers%20as%20possible.%20Unknowingly%2C%20I%20did%20the%20same.%20I%20was%20never%20a%20tomboy%20or%20enjoyed%20wearing%20denims%20but%20I%20would%20wear%20jeans%2C%20with%20a%20t-shirt%20and%20a%20loose%20shirt%20borrowed%20from%20my%20elder%20brother%E2%80%99s%20closet%20over%20it%2C%20thinking%20this%20would%20not%20catch%20attention.%20All%20these%20layers%20in%20north%20Indian%20summers%20which%20can%20easily%20touch%2045%C2%B0Celsius%20and%20riding%20a%20bicycle%20%E2%80%93%20I%20used%20to%20be%20drenched%20in%20sweat%20but%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20ever%20think%20of%20wearing%20a%20suit%20which%20is%20made%20of%20cotton%20and%20much%20more%20airy.%20Dresses%20were%20not%20even%20on%20the%20scene%20back%20in%20the%201990s%20in%20small%20towns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20that%20this%20self-afflicted%20torture%20helped%20anything.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24164751%2F1599px-Indian_Students_4616.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24164751%2F1599px-Indian_Students_4616.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24164751%2F1599px-Indian_Students_4616-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24164751%2F1599px-Indian_Students_4616-1024x680.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674593%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22797%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Biswarup%20Ganguly%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0%2C%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20were%20on%20a%20bicycle%2C%20guys%20had%20a%20thing%20called%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eside%20marna%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20basically%20them%20ramming%20their%20bicycle%20or%20scooter%20into%20your%20front%20tyre%20so%20that%20you%20fell.%20I%20still%20do%20not%20understand%20why%20teenage%20boys%20think%20this%20violence%20is%20funny.%20I%20have%20fallen%20so%20many%20times%20and%20been%20harassed%20during%20school%20days%20that%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20remember%20the%20count.%20If%20not%20this%2C%20then%20there%20were%20occasions%20when%20someone%20would%20come%20too%20close%20out%20of%20the%20blue%20and%20slap%20your%20breasts.%20The%20long%20term%20anger%20and%20resentment%20it%20builds%20in%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20body%20is%20not%20even%20explored.%20I%20hated%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20day%2C%20I%20was%20on%20my%20way%20to%20my%20friend%E2%80%99s%20place%20with%20her%2C%20both%20of%20us%20riding%20our%20bicycles%20when%20a%20group%20of%20teenage%20boys%2C%20heading%20the%20same%20way%20as%20us%2C%20formed%20a%20ring%20around%20us.%20One%20of%20the%20boys%20was%20about%20to%20hit%20my%20friend%2C%20and%20to%20save%20herself%2C%20she%20barged%20into%20me.%20It%20had%20rained%20very%20heavily%20just%20a%20little%20while%20before%20so%20I%20went%20skidding%20for%20quite%20a%20few%20feet.%20My%20skirt%20got%20torn%2C%20my%20knees%20and%20shin%20was%20deeply%20gashed%2C%20as%20were%20my%20elbows%20and%20hands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20guys%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20laughing%20and%20no%20passerby%20did%20anything%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20the%20norm%20in%20Karnal.%20I%20never%20witnessed%20one%20incident%20where%20any%20elderly%20person%20intervened.%20My%20friend%E2%80%99s%20mother%20cleaned%20my%20wounds%20and%20gave%20me%20one%20of%20her%20dresses%20to%20wear%20to%20go%20back%20home.%20I%20had%20to%20get%20a%20tetanus%20injection%20and%20for%20weeks%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20walk%20properly%20or%20move%20my%20elbow.%20This%20was%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20times%20I%20was%20thrown%20off%20my%20bicycle%20and%20hurt%20myself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-sexual-violence-bjp-apathy-patriarchy%5C%22%3EWhy%20Does%20Our%20Government%20Need%20a%20Graphic%20Depiction%20of%20Violence%20Against%20Women%20to%20Act%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20already%20started%20working%20before%20my%20mother%20retired%20from%20the%20school%2C%20and%20one%20time%20while%20I%20was%20visiting%20home%2C%20I%20went%20to%20pick%20her%20up%20in%20my%20car%20after%20school.%20I%20had%20studied%20in%20the%20same%20school%20and%20our%20uniform%20used%20to%20be%20a%20white%20shirt%2C%20navy%20blue%20skirt%20(for%20girls)%2C%20navy%20blue%20trousers%20for%20guys%2C%20along%20with%20a%20tie%20and%20belt.%20And%20black%20shoes.%20I%20used%20to%20love%20my%20uniform%20%E2%80%93%20carefully%20and%20perfectly%20creased%20pleated%20skirt%2C%20socks%20folded%20down%20with%20black%20mary-janes.%20I%20was%20waiting%20outside%20the%20school%20gate%20in%20the%20car%20for%20my%20mother%20when%20I%20saw%20girls%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20school%20in%20white%20kurta%2C%20navy%20blue%20salwar%20and%20navy%20blue%20dupatta.%20When%20my%20mother%20came%2C%20I%20asked%20her%20if%20some%20other%20school%20visiting%20or%20if%20there%20was%20some%20event%20at%20the%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20told%20me%20the%20uniform%20for%20girls%20had%20changed.%20From%20grade%20seven%20or%20eight%2C%20they%20were%20supposed%20to%20wear%20this%20now.%20No%20sex%20education%2C%20no%20education%20on%20consent%2C%20on%20respecting%20women%2C%20nothing%20on%20sexual%20violence%20%E2%80%93%20the%20solution%20was%20to%20cover%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20as%20they%20thought%20appropriate.%20Reinforcing%20objectification%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20right%20from%20school%20level%2C%20make%20it%20known%20to%20the%20world%20that%20this%20is%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20body%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20covered%20head%20to%20toe%20now%20%E2%80%93%20and%20yes%2C%20now%20available%20for%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20was%20maybe%20eight%20or%20nine%20years%20old%2C%20I%20went%20to%20visit%20a%20family%20friend%20with%20my%20mother%20on%20a%20cycle%20rickshaw.%20We%20were%20at%20a%20major%20crossing%20almost%20right%20in%20front%20of%20the%20town%20court%2C%20the%20office%20of%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20was%20quite%20literally%2010-15%20feet%20away%2C%20and%20there%20was%20the%20body%20of%20a%20young%20woman%20lying%20on%20the%20road.%20Nobody%20did%20anything.%20People%20were%20just%20looking%20at%20her%20and%20passing%20by.%20There%20was%20no%20policeman%20around.%20I%20was%20so%20horrified%20I%20started%20screaming%20at%20my%20mother.%20Why%20isn%E2%80%99t%20anyone%20doing%20anything%3F%20Why%20aren%E2%80%99t%20they%20taking%20her%20to%20hospital%3F%20She%20will%20die.%20My%20mother%20turned%20my%20face%20to%20the%20other%20side%20and%20said%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20already%20too%20late.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20woman%20was%20wearing%20a%20suit%20%E2%80%93%20white%20kameez%20and%20a%20worn%20out%20blue%20dupatta%20tightly%20covering%20her%20head%20and%20chest.%20That%20road%20led%20towards%20where%20poor%20Dalit%20families%20lived%20back%20then.%20Her%20lifeless%20body%20was%20still%20entangled%20in%20her%20rickety%20old%20bicycle%20she%20was%20riding%2C%20apparently%20pushed%20for%20fun%20by%20some%20guy%20causing%20her%20to%20hit%20her%20head%20on%20the%20pavement.%20What%20fun!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20days%20I%20kept%20thinking%20who%20would%20tell%20her%20family%2C%20did%20they%20know%2C%20what%20if%20she%20had%20small%20kids%20at%20home%2C%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20them%3F%20The%20image%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20stopped%20haunting%20me%20to%20this%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EParul%20Abrol%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695555389000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23101923%2FIMG_2534-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fwhat-does-a-dupatta-mean-for-a-young-woman%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wearing%20a%20salwar-kameez%20was%20like%20a%20clear%20signal%20to%20the%20world%20that%20this%20girl%20has%20grown%20up%20and%20is%20now%20available%20for%20harassment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fwhat-does-a-dupatta-mean-for-a-young-woman%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Prickly%20Nationalism%E2%80%99%3A%20From%20a%20G20%20High%20to%20a%20Post-Canada%20Low%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24171723%2FModi-Trudeau.png%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695555332000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19230651%2FH20230910138622.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fglobal-press-views-on-india-canada-row-nijjar-allegations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20against%20India%20have%20raised%20serious%20and%20disturbing%20questions%20about%20the%20Modi%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fglobal-press-views-on-india-canada-row-nijjar-allegations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20State%2C%20Formally%2C%20Remains%20Male%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24162044%2FF6kk7dtXkAEhH2a-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESaakhi%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20politics%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20in%20India%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20has%20typically%20been%20a%20politics%20of%20backlash%20against%20the%20inclusive%20socialism%20of%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance.%20Along%20these%20years%2C%20we%20have%20noticed%20a%20gradual%20nationalisation%20of%20the%20core%20ideology%20of%20the%20conservative%20Hindu%20family%20system%20where%20the%20man%20was%20the%20patriarch%20and%20the%20family%2C%20his%20property.%20Women%20were%20to%20be%20defined%20as%20mother%2C%20daughter%2C%20sister%20or%20%3Cem%3Ebhabi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sister-in-law)%20and%20the%20patriarchs%20laid%20down%20the%20law%2C%20both%20within%20homes%20and%20outside.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20326px)%2085vw%2C%20326px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22326%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22397%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20simultaneous%20dilution%20of%20earlier%20government%20programmes%20like%20the%20MGNREGA%20and%20food%20subsidies%2C%20along%20with%20substantial%20changes%20in%20the%20admission%20policies%2C%20syllabi%20and%20faculties%20in%20institutes%20of%20learning.%20All%20this%20slowly%20eroded%20much%20of%20the%20free%20choices%20that%20had%20become%20available%20to%20the%20women%20and%20the%20marginalised%20courtesy%20various%20rights%20movements%2C%20progressive%20laws%20and%20judgments%20from%20the%20apex%20court.%20During%20and%20after%20COVID-19%2C%20this%20resulted%20in%20major%20losses%20for%20working%20women%20in%20all%20categories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20this%20background%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-cabinet-clear-33-percent%5C%22%3Ethe%20law%20granting%2033%25%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20the%20legislature%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20certainly%20a%20positive%20step.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20law%2C%20conceptually%2C%20is%20three%20decades%20old%20and%20began%20stirring%20when%2033%25%20seats%20were%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Panchayati%20Raj%20system.%20The%20parties%20then%20in%20the%20opposition%20had%20declared%20it%20a%20non-starter%20but%20with%202024%20general%20elections%20looming%20large%20over%20the%20horizon%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20vote%20bank%20has%20an%20undeniable%20power%20of%20deciding%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20next%20government.%20The%20same%20rightwing%20that%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fkarnataka-cm-siddaramaiah-slams-centre-on-blocks-to-implementing-women-reservation-bill-2439719-2023-09-24%5C%22%3Eplayed%20a%20role%20in%20blocking%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%20chose%20to%20rebrand%20it%20as%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%20%E2%80%93%20a%20most%20progressive%20step%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20in%20Amrit%20Kaal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20voting%20on%20the%20Bill%2C%20all%20the%20well%20known%20female%20politician%20baiters%20within%20the%20legislative%20bodies%20and%20political%20parties%20thumped%20their%20tables%20in%20happy%20assent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20those%20who%20had%20registered%20their%20displeasure%20against%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20on%20grounds%20that%20so%20many%20strong%20wilful%20women%20would%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20our%20men%20and%20their%20masculinity%20(%3Cem%3Epaurush%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Epurusharth%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20were%20made%20to%20eat%20their%20words.%20Like%20chastened%20school%20boys%20when%20the%20bell%20rang%20all%20of%20them%20voted%20for%20the%20Bill%20as%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20remains%20that%20in%202024%20the%20powerful%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20leadership%20is%20pitted%20against%20two%20major%20female%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Sonia%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20with%20their%20vociferous%20troops%20of%20younger%20ones%20like%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%2C%20and%20Supriya%20Shrinate%2C%20with%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20bringing%20up%20the%20rear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20legal%20luminaries%20the%20new%20law%20is%20a%20positive%20step%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20implemented%20only%20after%20the%20Census%20(last%20held%20in%202011)%20and%20time%20consuming%20delimitation%20exercises%20are%20completed%20and%20their%20results%20calculated%20and%20announced%20formally.%20Then%20there%20is%20the%20question%20of%20the%20women%20in%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20communities.%20They%20want%20a%20quota%20within%20the%20new%20quota%20%E2%80%93%20same%20as%20their%20sisters%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20communities%20do.%20So%20nobody%20can%20tell%20the%20nation%20when%20the%20complex%20and%20time%20consuming%20exercises%20will%20begin%20and%20end%2C%20and%20how%20exactly%20the%20women%20in%20the%20OBC%20category%20will%20be%20included.%20Women%20should%20thus%20expect%20no%20miracles%20this%20once%20in%20ticket%20distribution.%20It%20will%20most%20probably%20be%20the%20same%20old%2C%20same%20old%20with%20a%20few%20usual%20freebies%20like%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flpg-price-cut-modis-rakhi-gift-ends-up-drawing-attention-to-inflation%5C%22%3E%20comparatively%20%E2%80%98cheaper%E2%80%99%20gas%20cylinders%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20grains%20thrown%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20interesting%20point%20concerns%20the%20contrast%20between%20repeated%20finger-wagging%20criticism%20of%20the%20dynasts%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20family%20will%20still%20be%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20first%20criteria%20for%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20selection%20as%20an%20electoral%20candidate.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBe%20it%20noted%20also%20how%20Bollywood%20actors%20storming%20in%20to%20fill%20the%20void%20created%20by%20feminists%20and%20liberals%20have%20been%20speaking%20into%20every%20available%20TV%20mic%20with%20gushing%20words%20of%20praise%20for%20the%20visionary%20new%20beginning%20for%20Nari%20Shakti%20or%20woman%20power.%20Their%20proximity%20to%20power%20might%20be%20an%20early%20indicator%20of%20which%20way%20the%20wind%20is%20blowing%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20woman%20candidates.%20For%20the%20time%20being%2C%20men%20remain%20the%20political%20gate-keepers%20in%20most%20parties.%20It%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20men%20of%20a%20certain%20age%20are%20likely%20to%20confess%20that%20women%20candidates%20in%20India%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20win%20unless%20backed%20by%20a%20powerful%20clan%20and%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.knightlab.com%2Flibs%2Ftimeline3%2Flatest%2Fembed%2Findex.html%3Fsource%3D1601B6of0DDLcqevG_UcSmg9POp-SSf0RVP-fHv36Cyk%26font%3DDefault%26lang%3Den%26initial_zoom%3D2%26height%3D650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20women%20in%20India%20have%20come%20a%20long%20way%20from%20our%20parliament%20of%201952.%20Then%2C%20out%20of%20the%20total%20499%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20mere%C2%A0%2022%20(4.41%25%20of%20the%20total)%20were%20occupied%20by%20women%20and%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20also%2C%20they%20numbered%20a%20mere%207.31%25%20of%20the%20total.%20Their%20numbers%20in%20the%20last%20(16%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ELok%20Sabha%20rose%20to%2011.23%25%20of%20all%20(543)%20seats%20and%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20they%20were%2011.62%25%20of%20the%20total%20number.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20But%20they%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20yet%20before%20they%20come%20anywhere%20near%20the%20present%20day%20number%20of%20women%20parliamentarians%20in%20some%20other%20developing%20countries.%20Even%20Rwanda%20(56.3%25)%20and%20our%20neighbouring%20Nepal%20(33.2%25)%20have%20higher%20figures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%20the%20NDA%2C%20led%20by%20the%20rightwing%20BJP%2C%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20an%20ebullient%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20assembled%20his%20most%20trusted%20brains%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20think-tank%20to%20create%20an%20image%20of%20his%20government%20as%20a%20progressive%20force.%20Empowerment%20of%20women%20was%20showcased%20by%20giving%20charge%20of%20the%20ministries%20of%20human%20resource%20development%2C%20finance%2C%20external%20affairs%2C%20food%20processing%2C%20and%20Ganga%20cleaning%20to%20women%20MPs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20for%20ordinary%20women%2C%20one%20of%20the%20key%20takeaways%20from%20the%20past%20five%20years%20of%20NDA%20rule%20has%20been%20that%20even%20powerful%20women%20within%20the%20ruling%20party%20may%20not%20get%20their%20due.%20Their%20frequent%20TV%20appearances%2C%20dazzling%20lives%20and%20participation%20in%20global%20dos%2C%20can%20barely%20hide%20a%20guaranteed%20obedience%20to%20the%20male%20leadership.%20Or%20else%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-media-wrestlers-protest-brij-bhushan-singh%5C%22%3Ewomen%20athletes%20were%20protesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20their%20abuse%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-video-survivors-petition%5C%22%3Etribal%20women%20paraded%20and%20groped%20naked%20on%20streets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20would%20not%20have%20remained%20silent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20storming%20into%20parliament%20alone%20can%20reveal%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India%2C%20how%20much%20of%20the%20state%20as%20we%20saw%20and%20experienced%20was%20determined%20by%20dominant%20social%20relations%20and%20the%20operative%20laws%20and%20instruments%20of%20a%20male%20state.%20If%20a%20state%20is%20built%20on%20the%20relative%20powerlessness%20of%2050%25%20of%20its%20citizens%2C%20(only%20one-tenth%20of%20whom%20are%20represented%20in%20the%20lawmaking%20legislative%20bodies)%2C%20could%20it%20ever%20see%20how%20male%20power%20in%20India%20(even%20in%20Amrit%20Kaal)%20is%20synonymous%20with%20state%20power%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20things%20stand%20today%2C%20and%20will%20during%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20formally%2C%20the%20state%20remains%20male.%20It%20will%20legitimise%20itself%20by%20imposing%20its%20own%20view%20of%20society%20as%20rational%20and%20the%20only%20acceptable%20one.%20Since%20the%20fabled%20reservation%20is%20perhaps%20not%20going%20to%20become%20a%20reality%20in%20the%20lifetime%20of%20my%20generation%2C%20we%20shall%2C%20until%20we%20live%2C%20be%20seeing%20women%20groups%20clustered%20around%20a%20beaming%20male%20PM%2C%20like%20happy%20sheep.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20finally%20do%2C%20women%20getting%2033%25%20reserved%20seats%20in%20parliament%20and%20assemblies%20will%20usher%20in%20a%20truly%20revolutionary%20scenario.%20Because%20as%20Thomas%20Kuhn%20wrote%2C%20true%20political%20revolutions%20will%20often%20change%20political%20institutes%20in%20ways%20that%20they%20themselves%20have%20prohibited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMrinal%20Pande%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695553014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24162044%2FF6kk7dtXkAEhH2a-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-parliament%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20a%20number%20of%20reasons%20why%20despite%20the%20women's%20reservation%20Bill%20becoming%20an%20Act%2C%20women%20should%20expect%20no%20miracles%20in%202024%2C%20in%20ticket%20distribution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-parliament%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Poisoned'%20meal%20survivor%20discharged%20from%20hospital%20two%20months%20after%20falling%20ill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695552540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-heather-wilkinson-ian-wilkinson_6245362.jpg%3F20230809130012%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsurvivor-of-mushroom-poisoning-meal-in-australia-discharged-from-hospital-12968851%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sole%20survivor%20from%20a%20group%20of%20people%20who%20ate%20a%20beef%20wellington%20meal%20laced%20with%20suspected%20poisonous%20mushrooms%20has%20been%20released%20from%20hospital%20-%20almost%20two%20months%20after%20falling%20ill.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A124%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsurvivor-of-mushroom-poisoning-meal-in-australia-discharged-from-hospital-12968851%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsurvivor-of-mushroom-poisoning-meal-in-australia-discharged-from-hospital-12968851%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsurvivor-of-mushroom-poisoning-meal-in-australia-discharged-from-hospital-12968851%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NASA%20returns%20largest%20asteroid%20sample%20to%20Earth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695549960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F70x70%2Fskynews-return-capsule-asteroid-bennu_6297581.jpg%3F20230925095717%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fosiris-rex-nasa-returns-sample-from-asteroid-bennu-to-earth-12968837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20NASA%20capsule%20carrying%20the%20largest%20sample%20ever%20collected%20from%20an%20asteroid%20has%20returned%20to%20Earth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A592%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fosiris-rex-nasa-returns-sample-from-asteroid-bennu-to-earth-12968837%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fosiris-rex-nasa-returns-sample-from-asteroid-bennu-to-earth-12968837%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fosiris-rex-nasa-returns-sample-from-asteroid-bennu-to-earth-12968837%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20New%20Building%20for%20Parliament%3A%20Body%20Without%20Soul%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24153155%2FF6ZBJaLbwAANsqu-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECommenting%20felicitously%20on%20what%20he%20has%20called%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cage%20of%20ambition%E2%80%9D%20scholar%20and%20commentator%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Mehta%20has%20characterised%20%E2%80%9Cinfrastructural%20nationalism%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20most%20dominantly%20visible%20feature%20of%20this%20ambition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeculating%20on%20how%20this%20new%20ambition%20is%20symbolised%20by%20an%20architectural%C2%A0assertion%2C%20Mehta%20wonders%20if%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emay%20also%20generate%20a%20new%C2%A0%E2%80%9Crighteousness%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20the%20answer%20seems%20to%20have%20found%20its%20way%20to%20us%2C%20sooner%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlas%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Crighteousness%E2%80%9D%20that%C2%A0%20was%20in%20evidence%20on%20Friday%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20not%20of%20the%20kind%20that%20Mehta%20may%20have%20had%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERogue%20brazenness%3A%20%E2%80%98Double%20engine%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20rogue%20brazenness%20at%20its%20best.%20Words%20hurled%20by%20a%20parliamentarian%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20a%20fellow%20parliamentarian%20from%20another%20party%2C%20who%20happened%20to%20be%20a%20Muslim%2C%20in%20a%20rush%20of%20abusive%2C%20sectarian%20invective%2C%20is%20best%20read%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-lok-sabha-hate-speech%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emedia%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20indeed%20%E2%80%9Crighteousness%E2%80%9D%20as%20condemnable%20hubris%20issuing%20from%20a%20new%20sense%20of%20historical%20conquest%20that%2C%20matching%20the%20grandeur%20of%20the%20new%20building%2C%20expressed%20itself%20as%20the%20contempt%20of%20the%20despot%20conqueror%20for%20the%20trampled%20adversary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cage%20of%20ambition%E2%80%9D%20that%20Mehta%20speaks%20of%20with%20perspicacity%20is%2C%20if%20I%20may%20be%20forgiven%2C%20harking%20back%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-does-bjps-metaphor-of-double-engine-ki-sarkar-signify%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eone%20of%20my%20earlier%20columns%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20best%20captured%20in%20the%20metaphor%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20engine%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20so%20often%20lauds%20and%20peddles%2C%20except%20that%20my%20use%20of%20the%20metaphor%20is%20widely%20(and%20wildly)%20different%20from%20the%20meaning%20the%20ruling%20party%20scions%C2%A0attach%20to%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20engine%20pulls%20fast%20forward%2C%20embracing%20every%20bit%20of%20the%20latest%20technology%20that%20science%20makes%20possible%2C%20all%20the%20way%20upto%20the%20south%20side%20of%20the%20moon%3B%20the%20other%20rushes%20the%20republic%20backward%20to%20the%20mythic%20glories%20of%20an%20ancient%20past%2C%20stamped%20most%20emphatically%20on%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20rover%20landed%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-landing-site-called-shiv-shakti-how-are-points-on-moon-named-101693181455182.html%5C%22%3EShiv-Shakti%20Sthal%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPut%20succinctly%2C%20the%20two%20engines%20denote%20two%20engines%20of%20the%20ruling%20right-wing%20ideology%20which%2C%20even%20if%20seen%20to%20be%20slightly%20different%20in%20direction%2C%20crucially%2C%20complement%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20trajectory%20to%20a%20common%20thesis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20during%20the%20crusades%2C%20the%20dominant%20ideological%20contour%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20age%20of%20ambition%E2%80%9D%20is%20to%20project%20material%20victories%20as%20the%20matching%20expression%20of%20the%20strengths%20of%20a%20new%20collective%C2%A0religious%20identity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20the%20message%20goes%2C%20we%20are%20conquering%20technologies%2C%20reaching%20the%20moon%E2%80%99s%20south%20pole%2C%20engaging%20start-ups%20of%20all%20kind%2C%20running%20ahead%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20economies%2C%20because%20we%20now%20know%20the%20power%20of%20being%20Hindus%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20could%20have%20been%20a%20more%20abrasively%20gauche%20demonstration%20of%C2%A0%20this%20concatenation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20current%20history%20than%20afforded%20by%20the%20right%20honourable%20MP%2C%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%2C%20who%20thought%20nothing%20of%20damning%20a%20fellow%20elected%20member%20in%20crass%2C%20hate-filled%20religious%20epithets%2C%20as%20if%20to%20say%2C%20you%20may%20be%20an%20elected%20representative%20too%2C%20but%20you%20now%20live%20on%20the%20sufferance%20of%20the%20ruling%20Hindu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20all%2C%20do%20recall%20what%20the%20honourable%20prime%20minister%20himself%20said%20when%20he%20first%20entered%20the%20portals%20of%20parliament%20in%202014%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20have%20achieved%20independence%20after%201200%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20if%20one%20engine%20is%20meant%20to%20scale%20the%20furthest%20reaches%20of%20technological%20modernity%2C%20the%20other%20is%20programmed%20to%20a%20revanchist%20agenda%20calculated%20to%20assert%20the%20glories%20of%20a%20cultural%20and%20religious%20past%2C%20versus%20the%20%E2%80%98Left-Liberal%20interregnum%E2%80%99%2C%20one%20that%20I%20define%20as%20the%20freedom%20movement%20and%C2%A0the%20six%C2%A0decades%20of%20rationalism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEgalitarian%20Democracy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%C2%A0struggling%20republic%C2%A0%20squeaks%2C%20to%20retain%20a%20semblance%20of%20an%20egalitarian%20democracy%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9C%20new%20age%20of%20ambition%E2%80%9D%20requires%20an%20unbridled%20centre%20of%20authority%20that%20is%20derived%20from%20a%20revived%20religious%2Fcultural%20assertion%20rather%20than%20from%20just%20universal%20adult%20franchise%20(although%20the%20latter%20may%20be%20retained%20as%20a%20necessary%20nuisance%20till%20the%20crusade%20fully%20reaches%20its%20culmination).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImagine%20for%20a%20moment%2C%20if%20what%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20has%20hurled%20at%20Danish%20Ali%20was%20hurled%20instead%20by%20Danish%20Ali%20at%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%3B%20would%20he%20just%20have%20been%20warned%20by%20the%20honourable%20Speaker%20to%20desist%20from%20repeating%20the%20offence%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20answer%20crossing%20your%20mind%20is%20the%20crisis%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20present%20moment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695549789000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24153155%2FF6ZBJaLbwAANsqu-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnew-parliament-ramesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-soul%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20is%20engaged%20in%20a%20fundamental%20task%20of%20taking%20down%20the%20idea%20of%20egalitarianism.%20If%20what%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20has%20hurled%20at%20Danish%20Ali%20was%20hurled%20instead%20by%20Ali%20at%20Bidhuri%2C%20would%20he%20have%20just%20been%20chided%20to%20not%20repeat%20it%3F%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnew-parliament-ramesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-soul%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Justice%20for%20Ganga%20Requires%20Urgent%20Collective%20Action%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24141720%2F1600px-The_Divine_Ganga_or_Ganges_River.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20last%20Sunday%20of%20September%20is%20observed%20as%20World%20Rivers%20Day.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20a%20coincidence%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fgovernment-forms-jal-shakti-ministry-by-merging-water-resources-and-drinking-water-ministries%2Farticleshow%2F69602462.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Echose%20to%20rename%20the%20water%20resource%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9CMinistry%20of%20Jal%20Shakti%E2%80%9D%20with%20divisions%20like%20the%20Department%20of%20Drinking%20Water%20and%20Sanitation%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Water%20Resources%2C%20River%20Development%20and%20Ganga%20Rejuvenation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20departmental%20groupings%20and%20name%20modifications%20each%20have%20their%20own%20importance%2C%20purpose%2C%20results%2C%20and%20effects.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20mission%20has%20been%20clarified%20by%20the%20new%20name%2C%20which%20also%20specifies%20that%20its%20primary%20goal%20going%20forward%20will%20be%20to%20analyse%20the%20value%20and%20power%20of%20water%20and%20will%20thus%20be%20administratively%20distinct%20from%20river%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20significant%20distinction%20is%20that%20the%20government%20has%20preserved%20the%20department%E2%80%99s%20name%20as%20the%20Department%20of%20River%20Development%20rather%20than%20renaming%20it%20as%20the%20River%20Basin%20Development.%20Here%2C%20the%20obvious%20goal%20is%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20development%20and%20preservation%20of%20the%20river%20herself%20is%20important%20and%20is%2C%20administratively%2C%20an%20independent%20activity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20India%2C%20where%20rivers%20are%20revered%20and%20treated%20as%20religious%20entities%2C%20such%20understanding%20cannot%20be%20subject%20to%20surprise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findias-water-governance-plan-cannot-leave-out-its-people%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Water%20Governance%20Plan%20Cannot%20Leave%20Out%20Its%20People%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20religious%20significance%20of%20rivers%20in%20India%20goes%20back%20centuries%20%E2%80%93%20Hindu%20priests%20have%20bathed%20in%20rivers%20like%20Ganga%2C%20Yamuna%20and%20Sarasvati%20and%20offered%20prayers%20along%20their%20banks.%20Given%20their%20religious%20significance%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20imagine%20that%20today%20these%20rivers%20are%20losing%20their%20famed%20purity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20fact%20has%20been%20highlighted%20multiple%20times%20by%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Board.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%20the%20board%20reported%20that%2046%25%20of%20Indian%20rivers%20are%20polluted.%20It%20has%20identified%20311%20polluted%20river%20stretches%20(PRS)%20on%20279%20different%20rivers%20in%2028%20different%20states%20and%208%20union%20territories.%20The%20board%20confirmed%20that%20Ganga%20is%20the%20most%20polluted%20river%20among%20all%20the%20others.%20In%20January%202023%2C%20dangerous%20amounts%20of%20faecal%20coliform%20were%20recorded%20by%20at%20least%2071%25%20of%20the%20Ganga%E2%80%99s%20monitoring%20stations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24142908%2FGanges-Brahmaputra-Meghna_basins.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24142908%2FGanges-Brahmaputra-Meghna_basins.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24142908%2FGanges-Brahmaputra-Meghna_basins-300x166.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24142908%2FGanges-Brahmaputra-Meghna_basins-1024x567.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674564%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22665%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMap%20outlining%20the%20states%20Ganga%20passes%20through.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20commons%2FPfly%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20concurs%2C%20listing%20Ganga%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20contaminated%20rivers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20saddest%20part%20is%20that%20this%20is%20the%20case%20even%20though%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20promised%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwork%20hard%E2%80%9D%20to%20purify%20the%20Ganga%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnmcg.nic.in%2FNamamiGanga.aspx%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Namami%20Gange%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20project%2C%20and%20even%20though%20the%20Union%20has%2C%20since%202014%2C%20taken%20on%20409%20projects%20with%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1898802%5C%22%3E%20budget%20outlay%20of%20Rs%2032%2C912.40%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20river%2C%20as%20the%20Jal%20Shakti%20ministry%20confirmed%20in%20February%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reports%20released%20by%20different%20institutions%20confirm%20that%20reality%20does%20not%20reflect%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpriority%20commitment%E2%80%9D%20made%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGanga%20Mata%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(mother%20Ganga).%20Open%20drains%20allow%20untreated%20sewage%20and%20other%20sorts%20of%20garbage%20to%20flow%20into%20the%20Ganga%2C%20turning%20the%20river%20crimson%20in%20some%20places%20and%20producing%20clouds%20of%20deadly%20foam%20floating%20on%20the%20river%E2%80%99s%20surface%20in%20others.%20This%20happens%20in%20spite%20of%20all%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20and%20pledges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECorruption%2C%20excessive%20bureaucracy%2C%20and%20the%20union%20government%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20utilise%20the%20entire%20sum%20allocated%20for%20development%20initiatives%20are%20frequently%20cited%20as%20the%20key%20causes%20of%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20ineffective%20performance.%20The%20argument%20is%20well-known%2C%20but%20curiously%2C%20the%20two%20most%20recent%20cases%20that%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20heard%20add%20to%20the%20narrative%20and%20reveal%20that%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20problem%20is%20more%20complex%20than%20it%20appears.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Friver-rejuvenation-ganga-blueprint%5C%22%3EGanga%20Still%20Suffers%20%E2%80%93%20But%20Govt%20Thinks%20%E2%80%98Successful%E2%80%99%20Rejuvenation%20Is%20a%20Blueprint%20for%20Other%20Rivers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20case%20titled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F80233351%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Subhas%20Datta%20vs.%20State%20of%20West%20Bengal%20%26amp%3B%20Others%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20the%20hotels%20and%20restaurants%20close%20to%20Howrah%20Railway%20Station%20were%20polluting%20the%20river%20Ganga%20with%20their%20liquid%20and%20solid%20waste.%20These%20constructions%20were%20allegedly%20illegal%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%20In%20another%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F97486486%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EManoj%20Kumar%20Rai%20vs.%20State%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20tribunal%20named%20local%20governments%20as%20being%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20Ganga%E2%80%99s%20pollution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tribunal%20declared%20that%20the%20state%20administration%20failed%20to%20hold%20negligent%20personnel%20accountable%20for%20the%20misappropriation%20of%20public%20funds%20and%20for%20failing%20to%20avoid%20harm%20to%20the%20Ganga%20river.%20The%20tribunal%20has%20taken%20seriously%20the%20discharge%20of%20about%2020%20million%20litres%2Fday%20(MLD)%20of%20untreated%20sewage%20into%20the%20Ganga%20by%20various%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20two%20cases%20demonstrate%20that%20a%20project%E2%80%99s%20failure%20is%20also%20because%20of%20the%20negligence%20of%20the%20private%20sector%20combined%20with%20the%20state%20administration%E2%80%99s%20failure.%20The%20two%20cases.%20and%20several%20more%20like%20them%2C%20show%20that%20in%20a%20federal%20structure%2C%20it%20is%20inappropriate%20to%20label%20every%20failure%20as%20that%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20identify%20individuals%2C%20groups%20and%20communities%20who%20contaminated%20the%20Ganga%20because%20Ganga%E2%80%99s%20waters%20flow%20through%20so%20many%20different%20states.%20Indeed%2C%20there%20are%20several%20parties%20responsible%20for%20the%20contamination%20of%20the%20river%2C%20and%20each%20has%20to%20be%20held%20accountable.%20However%2C%20regrettably%2C%20in%20India%2C%20politics%20is%20the%20sole%20lens%20used%20to%20observe%20and%20assess%20issues.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20is%20true%20that%20industrialisation%20is%20the%20primary%20cause%20of%20pollution%2C%20it%20is%20also%20true%20that%20religious%20and%20cultural%20ideals%20have%20not%20effectively%20promoted%20the%20concept%20and%20practice%20of%20revitalising%20the%20Ganga.%20Religious%20sentiments%20appreciate%20and%20support%20the%20Ganga%20as%20a%20living%20entity%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20things%20work%20the%20other%20way%20around.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24142128%2F6295950659_c93a8fe4bb_b.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24142128%2F6295950659_c93a8fe4bb_b.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24142128%2F6295950659_c93a8fe4bb_b-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674563%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EReligious%20rituals%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20Ganga.%20Photo%3A%20Flickr%2FCC%20By%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20should%20be%20no%20hesitation%20in%20admitting%20that%20other%20than%20industrialisation%2C%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20its%20contamination%20is%20related%20to%20its%20religious%20significance%20%E2%80%93%20immature%20and%20obscene%20ceremonies%20performed%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%20contribute%20to%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20project%E2%80%99s%20goals%20have%20not%20been%20met%20because%20the%20river%E2%80%99s%20water%20quality%20is%20constantly%20harmed%20by%20the%20immersion%20of%20idols%20and%20other%20religious%20objects%20during%20various%20festivals.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDevotees%2C%20while%20commemorating%20Ganga%E2%80%99s%20sacredness%2C%20rarely%20follow%20the%20guidelines%20outlined%20as%20part%20of%20the%20action%20plan%20for%20reviving%20Ganga.%20It%20is%20absolutely%20necessary%20in%20this%20situation%20to%20reinterpret%20ritualistic%20practices%20in%20order%20to%20encourage%20each%20Indian%20to%20see%20beyond%20themselves%20and%20safeguard%20the%20river%20from%20contamination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeeking%20to%20preserve%20the%20Ganga%20just%20because%20of%20her%20importance%20and%20utility%20is%20a%20widespread%20practice%2C%20however%2C%20it%20merely%20exemplifies%20human%20selfishness%20which%20compromise%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20river.%20This%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20further%20implies%20that%20Ganga%20should%20endure%20till%20it%20is%20beneficial%20to%20people.%20It%20is%20time%20that%20we%20went%20beyond%20self-serving%20motives%20and%20act%20collectively%20to%20save%20our%20rivers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Deepti%20Acharya%20is%20working%20as%20senior%20Assistant%20Professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Political%20Science%2C%20The%20Maharaja%20Sayajirao%20University%20of%20Baroda%2C%20Vadodara%20and%20author%20of%20the%20Book%20Water%20and%20Public%20Polices%20in%20India%2C%20Routledge%2C%20New%20York%20and%20London%2C%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695548833000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24141720%2F1600px-The_Divine_Ganga_or_Ganges_River.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2