ould%20take%20some%20time%20to%20digest%20that%20a%20woman%20was%20in%20command.%20I%20would%20often%20hear%20gossip%20and%20chattering%20behind%20my%20back%2C%20but%20I%20never%20let%20it%20bother%20me.%20The%20one%20advice%20to%20all%20women%20out%20there%20in%20such%20a%20setting%20would%20be%20to%20develop%20a%20Rhino-like%20thick%20skin%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20general%2C%20the%20mindset%20of%20male%20bosses%20or%20colleagues%20is%20that%20women%20are%20meant%20for%20%E2%80%98softer%E2%80%99%20jobs.%20They%20thought%20that%20women%20could%20not%20or%20should%20not%20put%20in%20extra%20hours%20as%20they%20would%20need%20to%20tend%20to%20children%20and%20families.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20have%20had%20to%20work%20extra%20hard%20to%20prove%20ourselves.%20But%20our%20assertiveness%20or%20proactive%20behaviour%20is%20often%20misconstrued%20as%20aggression%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sonali%20says%20that%20being%20in%20nature%20and%20among%20wildlife%20makes%20her%20job%20more%20fun%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330490%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2262