ctive%20administrator.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESonali%20also%20served%20a%20tenure%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Zoo%20in%20Delhi%20before%20she%20accepted%20the%20role%20at%20Kaziranga.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20Kaziranga%20her%20%3Cem%3EKarma%20Bhoomi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(land%20of%20action)%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshe%20fondly%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20career%20in%20the%20state%20at%20Kaziranga%20as%20a%20probationary%20trainee.%20At%20that%20time%20I%20was%2020%20years%20younger%20and%2020%20kg%20lighter!%20So%20when%20a%20rhino%20chased%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20the%20courage%20and%20strength%20to%20climb%20a%20tree!%20I%20dread%20what%20will%20happen%20now.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGhosh%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20a%20range%20of%20vital%20tasks%2C%20from%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%2C%20to%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20She%20also%20engages%20with%20local%20communities%2C%20delving%20into%20their%20reliance%20on%20the%20forest%20and%20exploring%20avenues%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F215138%2Fsustainable-e-commerce-karnival-shopping-online-eco-friendly-homegrown-products-lifestyle-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Ghosh's%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330492%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGhosh%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20Picture%20Credit%3A%20Sonali%20Ghosh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20role%20demands%20precise%20monitoring%20of%20wildlife%20through%20scientific%20techniques%20and%20the%20careful%20management%20of%20tourism%20through%20the%20creation%20and%20execution%20of%20ecotourism%20initiatives.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20her%20work%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20listener%20and%20understand%20how%20this%20famed%20protected%20area%20works.%20I%20have%20a%20great%20team%20with%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20forest%20frontline-to-area%20ratios%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20priority%20would%20be%20to%20continue%20with%20its%20protection%2C%20ensure%20and%20strengthen%20Rhinoceros%20and%20other%20flagship%20species%E2%80%99%20conservation.%20The%20second%20priority%20would%20be%20the%20utmost%20welfare%20of%20the%20forest%20frontline%20staff%20who%20serve%2024%C3%977%20in%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20conditions%20at%20Kaziranga%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20has%20only%20been%2020